#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:4
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:381
msgid "Commissions"
msgstr "Comisiones"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:6
msgid ""
"Commissions are payments made to employees that are earned as part of their "
"salary. The payments are awarded after a sale has been made, and the amount "
"depends on how much the sale was. Typically the amount is either a "
"percentage of the sale, or a set commission based on a structure created by "
"the company."
msgstr ""
"Las comisiones son pagos realizados a empleados que se ganan como parte de "
"su salario. Los pagos se otorgan después de realizar una venta, y el monto "
"depende de cuánto fue la venta. Normalmente, el monto es un porcentaje de la "
"venta o una comisión fija basada en una estructura creada por la empresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:11
msgid ""
"To pay an employee a commission they earned, a separate commission paycheck "
"must be issued to the employee. In Odoo, a commission payslip is referred to "
"as a *warrant payslip*."
msgstr ""
"Para pagar a un empleado una comisión que ganó, se debe emitir un recibo de "
"nómina de comisión separado al empleado. En Odoo, una nómina de comisión se "
"denomina *nómina de orden de pago*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:15
msgid "Create warrant payslips"
msgstr "Crear nóminas de orden de pago"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:17
msgid ""
"Warrant payslips are generated directly from the :guilabel:`Payslips "
"Batches` dashboard, which is accessed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Batches`."
msgstr ""
"Las nóminas de orden de pago se generan directamente desde el "
"tablero :guilabel:`Lotes de nóminas`, al que se accede navegando "
"a :menuselection:`aplicación Nómina --> Nóminas --> Lotes`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:20
msgid ""
"First, click the :guilabel:`Generate Warrant Payslips` button in the top-"
"left corner. Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Generate Warrant Payslips` pop-up "
"window, in which the necessary information **must** be filled out."
msgstr ""
"Primero, haz clic en el botón :guilabel:`Generar nóminas de orden de pago` "
"en la esquina superior izquierda. Al hacerlo, aparece una ventana "
"emergente :guilabel:`Generar nóminas de orden de pago`, en la que **debe** "
"completarse la información necesaria."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:24
msgid ""
"Set the time frame the commission was earned, in the two fields next "
"to :guilabel:`Period`. Click into each field, and a calendar pop-up window "
"loads. Navigate to the desired date and click on it to select it."
msgstr ""
"Establece el período en el que se ganó la comisión en los dos campos junto "
"a :guilabel:`Período`. Haz clic en cada campo y se carga una ventana "
"emergente de calendario. Navega hasta la fecha deseada y haz clic en ella "
"para seleccionarla."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:28
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the :guilabel:`Department` in the "
"corresponding field. When a department is selected, the employees listed for "
"that department appear in the :guilabel:`Employee` section, below."
msgstr ""
"Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona el :guilabel:`Departamento` en el "
"campo correspondiente. Cuando se selecciona un departamento, los empleados "
"listados para ese departamento aparecen en la sección :guilabel:`Empleado` "
"debajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:32
msgid ""
"If a file is needed for the record, upload a file to the :guilabel:`Import "
"File` field, such as a sales invoice, using the :guilabel:`Upload your file` "
"button. Any file type is accepted."
msgstr ""
"Si se necesita un archivo para el registro, carga un archivo en el "
"campo :guilabel:`Importar archivo`, como una factura de ventas, usando el "
"botón :guilabel:`Cargar tu archivo`. Se acepta cualquier tipo de archivo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:35
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Employee` section, enter the "
"individual :guilabel:`Commission Amount` for each employee in the far-right "
"column. To remove an employee, click the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon to remove the line."
msgstr ""
"En la sección :guilabel:`Empleado`, introduce el :guilabel:`Monto de "
"comisión` individual para cada empleado en la columna de la derecha. Para "
"eliminar un empleado, haz clic en el icono :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(papelera)` para eliminar la línea."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:39
msgid ""
"Add a new commission by clicking :guilabel:`Add a Line`, and entering "
"the :guilabel:`Employee` and the appropriate :guilabel:`Commission Amount`."
msgstr ""
"Añade una nueva comisión haciendo clic en :guilabel:`Añadir una línea` e "
"introduciendo el :guilabel:`Empleado` y el :guilabel:`Monto de comisión` "
"correspondiente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:42
msgid ""
"Once all the commissions are properly entered, click the :guilabel:`Generate "
"Payslips` button to create the warrant payslips in a group, which is "
"reffered to as a *pay run* in Odoo, or click :guilabel:`Export` to export a "
"CSV file of the commissions."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que todas las comisiones estén correctamente ingresadas, haz clic en "
"el botón :guilabel:`Generar nóminas` para crear las nóminas de garantía en "
"un grupo, lo cual se denomina *ejecución de nómina* en Odoo, o haz clic "
"en :guilabel:`Exportar` para exportar un archivo CSV de las comisiones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:46
msgid ""
":ref:`Process the pay run <payroll/pay-run-process>` in the same way as a "
"typical batch to complete the payment process."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Procesa la ejecución de nómina <payroll/pay-run-process>` de la misma "
"manera que un lote típico para completar el proceso de pago."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:None
msgid "Enter the commission details."
msgstr "Escriba los detalles de la comisión."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/commissions.rst:53
msgid ":doc:`Commissions <../../sales/sales/commissions>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Comisiones <../../sales/sales/commissions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:5
msgid ""
"Every employee in Odoo is required to have a running contract in order to be "
"paid. A contract outlines the terms of an employee's position, compensation, "
"working hours, and any other relevant terms."
msgstr ""
"Cada empleado en Odoo debe tener un contrato vigente para poder cobrar. Un "
"contrato describe los términos del puesto del empleado, compensación, horas "
"de trabajo y cualquier otro término relevante."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:9
msgid ""
"Contracts are created and managed in the *Payroll* tab of an :ref:`employee "
"record <employees/payroll>`. Employee records can be found by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Employees --> Employees`, or on the main "
"dashboard of the **Employees** app."
msgstr ""
"Los contratos se crean y gestionan en la pestaña *Nómina* de "
"un :ref:`registro de empleado <employees/payroll>`. Los registros de "
"empleados se pueden encontrar navegando a :menuselection:`Aplicación Nómina "
"--> Empleados --> Empleados`, o en el tablero principal de la aplicación "
"**Empleados**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:14
msgid ""
"Contract documents (PDFs) are uploaded and organized using the **Documents** "
"application, and are signed using the **Sign** application. Ensure these "
"applications are installed to send and sign contracts. Please refer to "
"the :doc:`../../productivity/documents` and :doc:`../../productivity/sign` "
"documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"Los documentos de contrato (PDF) se cargan y organizan usando la aplicación "
"**Documentos**, y se firman usando la aplicación **Firma electrónica**. "
"Asegúrate de que estas aplicaciones estén instaladas para enviar y firmar "
"contratos. Consulta la documentación de :doc:`../../productivity/documents` "
"y :doc:`../../productivity/sign` para más información."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:22
msgid "Create a contract"
msgstr "Crear un contrato"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:24
msgid ""
"Contracts are created by uploading a :ref:`contract template <payroll/"
"contract-template>` and making any necessary modifications for the specific "
"employee. Contract templates eliminate the need to configure new contracts "
"every time an employee is hired."
msgstr ""
"Los contratos se crean cargando una :ref:`plantilla de contrato <payroll/"
"contract-template>` y realizando las modificaciones necesarias para el "
"empleado específico. Las plantillas de contrato eliminan la necesidad de "
"configurar nuevos contratos cada vez que se contrata a un empleado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:28
msgid ""
"Contract templates are created through the configuration menu of the "
"**Payroll** or **Employees** apps and stored in the **Documents** app. If no "
"contract templates exist, or if a new contract template is "
"needed, :ref:`create a new template <payroll/contract-template>`."
msgstr ""
"Las plantillas de contrato se crean a través del menú de configuración de "
"las aplicaciones **Nómina** o **Empleados** y se almacenan en la aplicación "
"**Documentos**. Si no existen plantillas de contrato o se necesita una nueva "
"plantilla de contrato, :ref:`crea una nueva plantilla <payroll/contract-"
"template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:32
msgid ""
"Having multiple contract templates allows for faster contract creation for "
"commonly filled employment positions, such as full time, part time, "
"seasonal, etc."
msgstr ""
"Tener múltiples plantillas de contrato permite una creación más rápida de "
"contratos para puestos de empleo comúnmente ocupados, como tiempo completo, "
"tiempo parcial, temporada, etc."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create a new contract from a template, open the employee record and click "
"into the *Payroll* tab. Click :guilabel:`Load a Template`, and a *Contract "
"Template Load* pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"Para crear un nuevo contrato a partir de una plantilla, abre el registro del "
"empleado y haz clic en la pestaña *Nómina*. Haz clic en :guilabel:`Cargar "
"una plantilla`, y aparece una ventana emergente *Carga de plantilla de "
"contrato*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:38
msgid ""
"Using the drop-down menu, select the contract template for the employee, "
"then click :guilabel:`Load`. The various fields from the template populate "
"the corresponding fields in the *Payroll* tab, and the updates are recorded "
"in the chatter. Additional sections may appear, depending on the contract "
"template. Then, make any required modifications to the fields in the various "
"sections of the *Payroll* tab."
msgstr ""
"Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona la plantilla de contrato para el "
"empleado, luego haz clic en :guilabel:`Cargar`. Los diversos campos de la "
"plantilla rellenan los campos correspondientes en la pestaña *Nómina*, y las "
"actualizaciones se registran en el chatter. Pueden aparecer secciones "
"adicionales, según la plantilla de contrato. Luego, realiza las "
"modificaciones necesarias a los campos en las diversas secciones de la "
"pestaña *Nómina*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:45
msgid ""
"To access contract templates, the **Salary Configurator** "
"(`hr_contract_salary`) module **must** be :ref:`installed <general/"
"install>`. Depending on the installed :doc:`payroll localization "
"<payroll_localizations>`, different sections and fields may appear in the "
"*Payroll* tab."
msgstr ""
"Para acceder a las plantillas de contrato, el módulo **Configurador de "
"salarios** (`hr_contract_salary`) **debe** estar :ref:`instalado <general/"
"install>`. Dependiendo de la :doc:`localización de nómina "
"<payroll_localizations>` instalada, pueden aparecer diferentes secciones y "
"campos en la pestaña *Nómina*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:52
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:92
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:253
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:370
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:109
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:134
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:106
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:136
msgid "Contract overview section"
msgstr "Sección de resumen del contrato"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:54
msgid ""
"The only field *not* modified after loading a :ref:`contract template "
"<payroll/contract-template>` is the :guilabel:`Contract` field. This field "
"specifies the start date of the contract."
msgstr ""
"El único campo *no* modificado después de cargar una :ref:`plantilla de "
"contrato <payroll/contract-template>` es el campo :guilabel:`Contrato`. Este "
"campo especifica la fecha de inicio del contrato."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:57
msgid ""
"Click into the :guilabel:`Contract` field to reveal a calendar selector. "
"Click the start date for the contract. Once a date is selected, "
"a :guilabel:`to` field appears next to the start date. By "
"default, :guilabel:`Indefinite` is displayed in gray, indicating the "
"contract does not expire. If there is a set end date for the contract, click "
"into the :guilabel:`Indefinite` field, and click on the contract end date to "
"select it."
msgstr ""
"Haz clic en el campo :guilabel:`Contrato` para mostrar un selector de "
"calendario. Haz clic en la fecha de inicio del contrato. Una vez que se "
"selecciona una fecha, aparece un campo :guilabel:`hasta` junto a la fecha de "
"inicio. Por defecto, :guilabel:`Indefinido` se muestra en gris, indicando "
"que el contrato no expira. Si hay una fecha de finalización establecida para "
"el contrato, haz clic en el campo :guilabel:`Indefinido`, y haz clic en la "
"fecha de finalización del contrato para seleccionarla."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:64
msgid ""
"This field may remain blank if a start date is not known. Once the contract "
"is signed, that date is set as the :guilabel:`Start Date`."
msgstr ""
"Este campo puede permanecer en blanco si no se conoce una fecha de inicio. "
"Una vez que se firma el contrato, esa fecha se establece como "
"la :guilabel:`Fecha de inicio`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:70
msgid "Create contract templates"
msgstr "Crear plantillas de contrato"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:72
msgid ""
"To create a new contract template, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --"
"> Configuration --> Templates`, or :menuselection:`Employees app --> "
"Configuration --> Contract Templates`. Both methods open the *Contract "
"Templates* dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Para crear una nueva plantilla de contrato, navega "
"a :menuselection:`Aplicación Nómina --> Configuración --> Plantillas`, "
"o :menuselection:`Aplicación Empleados --> Configuración --> Plantillas de "
"contrato`. Ambos métodos abren el tablero *Plantillas de contrato*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:76
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button, and a blank contract template form loads. "
"Configure the following fields in the various sections of the form:"
msgstr ""
"Haz clic en el botón :guilabel:`Nuevo`, y se carga un formulario de "
"plantilla de contrato en blanco. Configura los siguientes campos en las "
"diversas secciones del formulario:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/work_entries.rst:252
#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:35
msgid "General information section"
msgstr "Sección de información general"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Template Name`: Enter a brief descriptive name for the template. "
"This should be clear and easily understood, as this name appears in the "
"**Recruitment** application, as well."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nombre de plantilla`: Introduce un nombre descriptivo breve para "
"la plantilla. Debe ser claro y fácilmente comprensible, ya que este nombre "
"aparece también en la aplicación **Reclutamiento**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Job`: Select the :doc:`job position <../recruitment/new_job>` the "
"contract template applies to from the drop-down menu. If blank, the template "
"applies to all job positions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Puesto de trabajo`: Selecciona el :doc:`puesto de trabajo <../"
"recruitment/new_job>` al que se aplica la plantilla de contrato desde el "
"menú desplegable. Si está en blanco, la plantilla se aplica a todos los "
"puestos de trabajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Department`: Select the department the contract template applies "
"to from the drop-down menu. If blank, the template applies to all "
"departments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Departamento`: Selecciona el departamento al que se aplica la "
"plantilla de contrato del menú desplegable. Si está en blanco, la plantilla "
"se aplica a todos los departamentos."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HR Responsible`: Select the employee responsible for validating "
"contracts, using this template, using the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Responsable de RR.HH.`: Selecciona el empleado responsable de "
"validar los contratos, usando esta plantilla, mediante el menú desplegable."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage Type`: Select either :guilabel:`Fixed Wage` "
"or :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` from the drop-down menu. Select :guilabel:`Fixed "
"Wage` for salaried employees, and select :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` for "
"employees who are paid based on their logged work hours."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipo de salario`: Selecciona :guilabel:`Salario fijo` "
"o :guilabel:`Salario por hora` del menú desplegable. "
"Selecciona :guilabel:`Salario fijo` para empleados asalariados, y "
"selecciona :guilabel:`Salario por hora` para empleados que cobran según las "
"horas de trabajo registradas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:97
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pay Schedule`: Using the drop-down menu, select how often the "
"employee is paid. The default options are: :guilabel:`year`, :guilabel:`half-"
"year`, :guilabel:`quarter`, :guilabel:`2 "
"months`, :guilabel:`month`, :guilabel:`half-month`, :guilabel:`2 "
"weeks`, :guilabel:`week`, or :guilabel:`day`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Calendario de pago`: Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona con "
"qué frecuencia se paga al empleado. Las opciones predeterminadas "
"son: :guilabel:`año`, :guilabel:`semestre`, :guilabel:`trimestre`, :guilabel:`2 "
"meses`, :guilabel:`mes`, :guilabel:`quincena`, :guilabel:`2 "
"semanas`, :guilabel:`semana`, o :guilabel:`día`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage`: Enter the gross wage. The time period presented in this "
"field  reflects what is selected for the :guilabel:`Pay Schedule` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salario`: Introduce el salario bruto. El período de tiempo "
"presentado en este campo refleja lo que está seleccionado en el "
"campo :guilabel:`Calendario de pago`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:105
msgid ""
"It is recommended to populate the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` field "
"*first*, since that value is used to automatically calculate "
"the :guilabel:`Wage`. If the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` is updated, "
"the :guilabel:`Wage` field updates as well."
msgstr ""
"Se recomienda rellenar *primero* el campo :guilabel:`Coste anual (real)`, ya "
"que ese valor se utiliza para calcular automáticamente "
"el :guilabel:`Salario`. Si se actualiza el :guilabel:`Coste anual (real)`, "
"el campo :guilabel:`Salario` también se actualiza."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select one of the 18 "
"default types of contracts. This list is the same as the *employment type*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipo de contrato`: Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona uno de "
"los 18 tipos de contratos predeterminados. Esta lista es la misma que el "
"*tipo de empleo*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:111
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pay Category`: Select one of the default pay categories using the "
"drop-down menu. The default pay categories are :guilabel:`Employee` "
"or :guilabel:`Worker`, which are pulled from the configured *salary "
"structures* in the **Payroll** app. A :ref:`new pay category <payroll/new-"
"structure-type>` can be created, if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Categoría salarial`: Selecciona una de las categorías salariales "
"predeterminadas usando el menú desplegable. Las categorías salariales "
"predeterminadas son :guilabel:`Empleado` o :guilabel:`Trabajador`, que se "
"extraen de las *estructuras salariales* configuradas en la aplicación "
"**Nómina**. Se puede crear una :ref:`nueva categoría salarial <payroll/new-"
"structure-type>` si es necesario."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:117
msgid ""
"In previous versions of Odoo, the :guilabel:`Pay category` was "
"called :guilabel:`Salary Structure Types`."
msgstr ""
"En versiones anteriores de Odoo, la :guilabel:`Categoría salarial` se "
"llamaba :guilabel:`Tipos de estructura salarial`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:120
msgid ""
"To view, modify, or add pay categories, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Configuration --> Structure Types`."
msgstr ""
"Para ver, modificar o añadir categorías salariales, navega "
"a :menuselection:`Aplicación Nómina --> Configuración --> Tipos de "
"estructura`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:123
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Pay Category` drop-down menu displays all the available "
"working schedules. To modify or add to this list, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Working Schedules`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New`, and create a new working schedule, or click on an "
"existing working schedule and make edits."
msgstr ""
"El menú desplegable :guilabel:`Categoría salarial` muestra todos los "
"horarios de trabajo disponibles. Para modificar o añadir a esta lista, "
"navega a :menuselection:`Aplicación Nómina --> Configuración --> Horarios de "
"trabajo`. Haz clic en :guilabel:`Nuevo`, y crea un nuevo horario de trabajo, "
"o haz clic en un horario de trabajo existente y realiza modificaciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:129
msgid "Employer costs section"
msgstr "Sección de costes del empleador"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Yearly Cost`: Enter the total yearly cost the employee costs the "
"employer. When this value is entered, the :guilabel:`Monthly Cost` "
"and :guilabel:`Wage` fields are automatically updated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Coste anual`: Introduce el coste anual total que el empleado "
"supone para el empleador. Cuando se introduce este valor, los "
"campos :guilabel:`Coste mensual` y :guilabel:`Salario` se actualizan "
"automáticamente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monthly Cost`: This field is **not** editable. The value is "
"automatically populated after the :guilabel:`Yearly Cost (Real)` is entered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Coste mensual`: Este campo **no** es editable. El valor se "
"completa automáticamente después de introducir el :guilabel:`Coste anual "
"(real)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:138
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Wage`, :guilabel:`Yearly Cost`, and :guilabel:`Monthly Cost` "
"fields are all linked. If any of these fields are updated, the other two "
"fields automatically update to reflect the change. It is best practice to "
"check these three fields if any modifications have been made, to ensure they "
"are accurate."
msgstr ""
"Los campos :guilabel:`Salario`, :guilabel:`Coste anual`, y :guilabel:`Coste "
"mensual` están vinculados. Si se actualiza cualquiera de estos campos, los "
"otros dos se actualizan automáticamente para reflejar el cambio. Es una "
"buena práctica verificar estos tres campos si se han realizado "
"modificaciones, para asegurar que son precisos."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:143
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage on Signature`: Enter the monthly wage in the field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salario en la firma`: Introduce el salario mensual en el campo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:146
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:303
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:388
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:139
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:167
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:134
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:121
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:168
msgid "Schedule section"
msgstr "Sección de horario"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:148
msgid ""
"Configure the following two fields in this section, to configure when the "
"employee is expected to work:"
msgstr ""
"Configura los siguientes dos campos en esta sección para configurar cuándo "
"se espera que el empleado trabaje:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Source`: Using the drop-down menu, select how "
"the :doc:`work entries <work_entries>` are generated. This field is "
"**required**. The options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fuente de entrada de trabajo`: Usando el menú desplegable, "
"selecciona cómo se generan las :doc:`entradas de trabajo <work_entries>`. "
"Este campo es **obligatorio**. Las opciones son:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:156
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Schedule`: Work entries are generated based on the "
"selected :guilabel:`Working Schedule`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Horario de trabajo`: Las entradas de trabajo se generan según "
"el :guilabel:`Horario de trabajo` seleccionado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:158
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Attendances`: Work entries are generated based on the employee's "
"check-in records in the **Attendances** app. (This requires the "
"**Attendances** app to be installed)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Asistencias`: Las entradas de trabajo se generan según los "
"registros de entrada del empleado en la aplicación **Asistencias**. (Esto "
"requiere que la aplicación **Asistencias** esté instalada)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:160
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Planning`: Work entries are generated based on the planned "
"schedule for the employee from the **Planning** app. (This requires the "
"**Planning** app to be installed)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planificación`: Las entradas de trabajo se generan según el "
"horario planificado para el empleado desde la aplicación **Planificación**. "
"(Esto requiere que la aplicación **Planificación** esté instalada)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:163
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: Select one of the available :guilabel:`Working "
"Hours` the employee is expected to work, using the drop-down menu. The "
"selected working hours determine how :doc:`work entries <work_entries>` are "
"generated, which determines the employees schedule and compensation. If this "
"field is left blank, the employee can work as many or as few hours as "
"desired each week, with no restrictions. The default options "
"are :guilabel:`Standard 40 hours/week`, and :guilabel:`Appointment Resource "
"Default Calendar`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Horario de trabajo`: Selecciona uno de los :guilabel:`Horarios de "
"trabajo` disponibles que se espera que el empleado trabaje, usando el menú "
"desplegable. El horario de trabajo seleccionado determina cómo se generan "
"las :doc:`entradas de trabajo <work_entries>`, lo que determina el "
"calendario y la compensación del empleado. Si este campo se deja en blanco, "
"el empleado puede trabajar tantas o tan pocas horas como desee cada semana, "
"sin restricciones. Las opciones predeterminadas son :guilabel:`Estándar 40 "
"horas/semana`, y :guilabel:`Calendario predeterminado de recurso de citas`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:171
msgid ""
"In previous versions of Odoo, :guilabel:`Working Hours` were "
"called :guilabel:`Working Schedules`."
msgstr ""
"En versiones anteriores de Odoo, :guilabel:`Horario de trabajo` se "
"llamaba :guilabel:`Calendarios de trabajo`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:175
msgid "Benefits and deductions"
msgstr "Beneficios y deducciones"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:177
msgid ""
"Depending on the :doc:`payroll localization <payroll_localizations>` for the "
"company, the remaining sections either vary, or may not appear at all. For "
"example, some entries may pertain to retirement accounts, health insurance "
"benefits, and commuter benefits."
msgstr ""
"Dependiendo de la :doc:`localización de nómina <payroll_localizations>` de "
"la empresa, las secciones restantes varían o pueden no aparecer en absoluto. "
"Por ejemplo, algunas entradas pueden referirse a cuentas de jubilación, "
"beneficios de seguro médico y beneficios de transporte."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:181
msgid ""
"Enter the monetary amounts or percentages to specify how much of the "
"employee's salary goes to the various benefits and deductions."
msgstr ""
"Introduce los montos monetarios o porcentajes para especificar cuánto del "
"salario del empleado se destina a los diversos beneficios y deducciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:185
msgid "Signatories tab"
msgstr "Pestaña de signatarios"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:187
msgid ""
"This tab outlines which contract template to use when creating a new "
"contract for an employee, and which to use when updating an existing "
"contract. This section also outlines which signatures are required.  "
"Configure the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Esta pestaña describe qué plantilla de contrato usar al crear un nuevo "
"contrato para un empleado, y cuál usar al actualizar un contrato existente. "
"Esta sección también describe qué firmas son necesarias. Configura los "
"siguientes campos:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:191
msgid ""
"New Contract :guilabel:`PDF Template`: Select the default PDF that a new "
"employee has to sign to accept an offer."
msgstr ""
"Plantilla PDF de :guilabel:`nuevo contrato`: Selecciona el PDF "
"predeterminado que un nuevo empleado debe firmar para aceptar una oferta."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:193
msgid ""
"Contract Update :guilabel:`PDF Template`: Select the default PDF that a "
"current employee has to sign to update their contract."
msgstr ""
"Plantilla PDF de :guilabel:`actualización de contrato`: Selecciona el PDF "
"predeterminado que un empleado actual debe firmar para actualizar su "
"contrato."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:196
msgid "Once a PDF contract is uploaded, the following fields appear:"
msgstr "Una vez que se carga un contrato PDF, aparecen los siguientes campos:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:198
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Role`: The label of the signature field to be signed. "
"This field is configured on the PDF itself, through the **Sign** app, and "
"cannot be modified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rol del contrato`: La etiqueta del campo de firma que debe "
"firmarse. Este campo se configura en el propio PDF, a través de la "
"aplicación **Firma electrónica**, y no se puede modificar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:200
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Signatory`: Using the drop-down menu, select the person who must "
"sign for the :guilabel:`Contract Role`. The default options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Firmante`: Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona la persona que "
"debe firmar para el :guilabel:`Rol del contrato`. Las opciones "
"predeterminadas son:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:203
msgid ":guilabel:`Employee`: Select this for the employee to sign the field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Empleado`: Selecciona esto para que el empleado firme el campo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:204
msgid ""
":guilabel:`HR Responsible`: Select this to specify the user listed as "
"the :guilabel:`HR Responsible` on the job position."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Responsable de RR. HH.`: Selecciona esto para especificar el "
"usuario listado como :guilabel:`Responsable de RR. HH.` en el puesto de "
"trabajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Specific Partner`: Select this to have a specific individual sign "
"the contract. When selected, the :guilabel:`Partner` field becomes active. "
"Using the drop-down menu, select the specific user who must sign the "
"contract in the :guilabel:`Partner` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Contacto específico`: Selecciona esto para que una persona "
"específica firme el contrato. Cuando se selecciona, el "
"campo :guilabel:`Contacto` se activa. Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona "
"el usuario específico que debe firmar el contrato en el "
"campo :guilabel:`Contacto`."

