msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:412
msgid ""
"A super account is the term for an Australian retirement savings account. "
"This tab houses the employee's various retirement accounts, or *super funds*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:416
msgid ""
"If an employee has an *Extra Negotiated Super*, *Extra Compulsory Super*, or "
"*Salary Sacrifice Superannuation,* these configuration can be found under "
