#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:483
msgid ":guilabel:`BSB`: Enter the Bank State Branch code in this field."
msgstr ":guilabel:`BSB`: Introduce el código Bank State Branch en este campo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:484
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account Holder`: Using the drop-down menu, select the "
"corresponding **Contact** app record for the account holder, typically the "
"company."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Titular de la cuenta`: Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona el "
"registro correspondiente de la aplicación **Contactos** para el titular de "
"la cuenta, normalmente la empresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:486
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account Holder Name`: The selected :guilabel:`Account Holder` "
"populates this field by default. Make any necessary modifications."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nombre del titular de la cuenta`: El :guilabel:`Titular de la "
