"modificaciones necesarias."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:488
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank`: Using the drop-down menu, select the bank the account is "
"under. Once selected, a *Bank Information* tab appears, containing the "
"various bank information. Make any desired edits to this tab."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Banco`: Usando el menú desplegable, selecciona el banco al que "
"pertenece la cuenta. Una vez seleccionado, aparece una pestaña *Información "
