#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:325
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:371
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:359
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:250
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:175
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:405
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:421
msgid "Rule parameters"
msgstr "Parámetros de regla"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:541
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:373
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:252
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:407
msgid ""
"Some calculations require specific rates associated with them, or wage caps. "
"*Rules Parameters* are capable of listing a value, either a percentage or a "
"fixed amount, to reference in the salary rules."
msgstr ""
"Algunos cálculos requieren tasas específicas asociadas con ellos, o topes "
"salariales. Los *Parámetros de reglas* pueden listar un valor, ya sea un "
"porcentaje o una cantidad fija, para referenciar en las reglas salariales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:544
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:380
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:365
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:255
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:414
msgid ""
"Most rules pull information stored in the parameters module to get the rate "
"of the rule (a percentage) and the cap (a dollar amount)."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de las reglas obtienen información almacenada en el módulo de "
"parámetros para conseguir la tasa de la regla (un porcentaje) y el tope (una "
"cantidad en dólares)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:547
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:383
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:368
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:258
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:183
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:417
msgid ""
"To view rule parameters, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Configuration --> Rule Parameters`. Here, all rule parameters are displayed "
"with their linked :guilabel:`Salary Rules`, which can be accessed. Review "
"the parameters associated with a rule by looking for the :guilabel:`Name` of "
"the rule, and make any edits as needed."
msgstr ""
"Para ver los parámetros de reglas, navega a :menuselection:`aplicación "
"Nómina --> Configuración --> Parámetros de reglas`. Aquí se muestran todos "
"los parámetros de reglas con sus :guilabel:`Reglas salariales` vinculadas, a "
"las que se puede acceder. Revisa los parámetros asociados con una regla "
"buscando el :guilabel:`Nombre` de la regla, y realiza las ediciones "
"necesarias."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:553
msgid ""
"Odoo adds updated rule parameters for the current calendar year. It is "
"**not** recommended to edit rule parameters **unless a national or local "
"parameter has changed**, and is different from the rule parameters created "
"by Odoo. Check with all local and national regulations *before* making any "
"changes to rule parameters."
msgstr ""
"Odoo añade parámetros de reglas actualizados para el año calendario actual. "
"**No** se recomienda editar los parámetros de reglas **a menos que un "
"parámetro nacional o local haya cambiado** y sea diferente de los parámetros "
"de reglas creados por Odoo. Consulta todas las regulaciones locales y "
"nacionales *antes* de realizar cambios en los parámetros de reglas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:559
msgid "Payroll onboarding"
msgstr "Incorporación de nómina"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:561
msgid ""
"Once the :ref:`company <payroll/payroll_localizations/au_gen>`, "
"the :ref:`STP responsible employee <payroll/payroll_localizations/stp>`, and "
"the :ref:`bank journal for direct debit <payroll/payroll_localizations/"
"bank_journals>` are configured, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Configurations --> Settings` to start the onboarding process."
msgstr ""
"Una vez configurados la :ref:`empresa <payroll/payroll_localizations/"
"au_gen>`, el :ref:`empleado responsable de STP <payroll/"
"payroll_localizations/stp>` y el :ref:`diario bancario para débito directo "
"<payroll/payroll_localizations/bank_journals>`, navega "
"a :menuselection:`Aplicación Nómina --> Configuración --> Ajustes` para "
"iniciar el proceso de incorporación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:566
msgid ""
"Scroll to the *Australian Localization* section, and under *SuperStream and "
"Single Touch Payroll*, select the :guilabel:`Payroll Mode`. "
"Choose :guilabel:`Production` for a production database with a valid "
"subscription code, or otherwise, select :guilabel:`Testing`. Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`Start Payroll Onboarding` button, and a *Payroll Onboarding* "
"pop-up window loads."
msgstr ""
"Desplázate a la sección *Localización australiana* y, en *SuperStream y "
"Single Touch Payroll*, selecciona el :guilabel:`Modo de nómina`. "
"Elige :guilabel:`Producción` para una base de datos de producción con un "
"código de suscripción válido, o de lo contrario, "
"selecciona :guilabel:`Pruebas`. Luego, haz clic en el "
"botón :guilabel:`Iniciar integración de nómina` y se cargará una ventana "
"emergente de *Integración de nómina*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:572
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended to test payroll on the testing database prior to "
"configuring the production environment, as any payroll processed in the "
"production database will be submitted directly to the |ATO|."
msgstr ""
"Se recomienda encarecidamente probar la nómina en la base de datos de "
"pruebas antes de configurar el entorno de producción, ya que cualquier "
"nómina procesada en la base de datos de producción se enviará directamente a "
"|ATO|."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:576
msgid ""
"On the *Payroll Responsible* stage, select the :ref:`STP responsible "
"employee <payroll/payroll_localizations/stp>` in the :guilabel:`Payroll "
"Responsible` field, then click the :guilabel:`Next Step` button."
msgstr ""
"En la etapa *Responsable de nómina*, selecciona el :ref:`empleado "
"responsable de STP <payroll/payroll_localizations/stp>` en el "
"campo :guilabel:`Responsable de nómina`, luego haz clic en el "
"botón :guilabel:`Siguiente paso`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:580
msgid ""
"On the *Authorised* stage, click the :guilabel:`Yes` option for the "
"question :guilabel:`Are you authorised to register for this service on "
"behalf of your employer`, then click the :guilabel:`Next Step` button."
msgstr ""
"En la etapa *Autorizado*, haz clic en la opción :guilabel:`Sí` para la "
"pregunta :guilabel:`¿Estás autorizado para registrarte en este servicio en "
"nombre de tu empleador?`, luego haz clic en el botón :guilabel:`Siguiente "
"paso`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:584
msgid ""
"On the *Employee Details* stage, review the business details and ensure they "
"are all correct, then click :guilabel:`Next Step`."
msgstr ""
"En la etapa *Detalles del empleado*, revisa los detalles de la empresa y "
"asegúrate de que todos sean correctos, luego haz clic "
"en :guilabel:`Siguiente paso`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:587
msgid ""
"On the *Bank Details* stage, select the company's :ref:`Bank journal "
"<payroll/payroll_localizations/bank_journals>` for direct debit, then "
"click :guilabel:`Next Step`."
msgstr ""
"En la etapa *Detalles bancarios*, selecciona el :ref:`Diario bancario "
"<payroll/payroll_localizations/bank_journals>` de la empresa para débito "
"directo, luego haz clic en :guilabel:`Siguiente paso`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:590
msgid "On the *Signature* stage, read the following PDF's:"
msgstr "En la etapa *Firma*, lee los siguientes PDF:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:592
msgid "Odoo's Terms & Conditions"
msgstr "Términos y condiciones de Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:593
msgid "SuperChoice FSG PDS DDA"
msgstr "SuperChoice FSG PDS DDA"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:595
msgid ""
"After the documents have been reviewed, click the two check boxes attesting "
"that the documents have been read, then, click the :guilabel:`Register` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Después de revisar los documentos, marca las dos casillas de verificación "
"que certifican que se han leído los documentos y luego haz clic en el "
"botón :guilabel:`Registrar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:599
msgid "Read the provided documents carefully before signing."
msgstr "Lee los documentos proporcionados con atención antes de firmar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:601
msgid ""
"Lastly, Odoo will provide advice on how to proceed in case the company needs "
"to switch from another |STP| software to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Por último, Odoo proporcionará consejos sobre cómo proceder en caso de que "
"la empresa necesite cambiar de otro software |STP| a Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:604
msgid ""
"On the *Import YTD Balances* pop-up window, select :guilabel:`Zeroed "
"Previous Payroll` if the previous payroll system has been zeroed out, or if "
"there is no previous payroll system. Next, enter the :guilabel:`Previous BMS "
"ID` in the corresponding field."
msgstr ""
"En la ventana emergente *Importar saldos YTD*, selecciona :guilabel:`Nómina "
"anterior puesta a cero` si el sistema de nómina anterior se ha puesto a "
"cero, o si no hay un sistema de nómina anterior. A continuación, introduce "
"el :guilabel:`ID de BMS anterior` en el campo correspondiente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:609
msgid ""
":guilabel:`BMS ID` is the *Business Management System Identifier* for your "
"organisation in the payroll system. This is important when transitioning "
"from other payroll systems to Odoo, as it ensures employees maintain "
"continuous year-to-date records on their payslips and |ATO| Portal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID de BMS` es el *Identificador del sistema de gestión "
"empresarial* para tu organización en el sistema de nómina. Esto es "
"importante al hacer la transición desde otros sistemas de nómina a Odoo, ya "
"que garantiza que los empleados mantengan registros continuos acumulados del "
"año en sus nóminas y en el Portal |ATO|."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:613
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Fiscal Year Start Date` in the corresponding field, "
"then click the :guilabel:`Transfer and Generate YTD` button."
msgstr ""
"Introduce la :guilabel:`Fecha de inicio del año fiscal` en el campo "
"correspondiente, luego haz clic en el botón :guilabel:`Transferir y generar "
"YTD`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:617
msgid "Importing YTD balances"
msgstr "Importar saldos YTD"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:619
msgid ""
"To import the year-to-date balances, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app "
"--> Configuration --> YTD Opening Balances`."
msgstr ""
"Para importar los saldos acumulados del año, navega "
"a :menuselection:`Aplicación de nómina --> Configuración --> Saldos de "
"apertura YTD`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:622
msgid ""
"After importing the YTD balances from the previous software, the |ATO| needs "
"to be notified of the change of BMS ID and payroll IDs. This step does not "
"apply for strategy 1."
msgstr ""
"Después de importar los saldos YTD del software anterior, es necesario "
"notificar a |ATO| el cambio de ID de BMS e ID de nómina. Este paso no aplica "
"para la estrategia 1."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:625
msgid ""
"To do so, after importing YTD balances, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Reporting --> Single Touch Payroll`, and submit the update event "
"created for this purpose."
msgstr ""
"Para hacerlo, después de importar los saldos YTD, navega "
"a :menuselection:`Aplicación de nómina --> Informes --> Single Touch "
"Payroll`, y envía el evento de actualización creado para este propósito."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:628
msgid ""
"Once the update event submitted to the |ATO|, pay runs and payslips can be "
"created for employees."
msgstr ""
"Una vez enviado el evento de actualización a |ATO|, se pueden crear períodos "
"de pago y nóminas para los empleados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:631
msgid "Run Australian payroll"
msgstr "Ejecutar nómina australiana"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:633
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:397
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:409
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:285
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:339
msgid ""
"Before running payroll, the payroll officer must validate "
"employee :doc:`work entries <../work_entries>` to confirm pay accuracy and "
"catch errors. This includes checking that all time off is approved and any "
"overtime is appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Antes de ejecutar la nómina, el responsable de nómina debe validar "
"las :doc:`entradas de trabajo <../work_entries>` del empleado para confirmar "
"la precisión del pago y detectar errores. Esto incluye verificar que todas "
"las ausencias estén aprobadas y que cualquier hora extra sea apropiada."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:637
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:401
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:413
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:289
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:343
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:441
msgid ""
"Work entries sync based on the employee's :doc:`contract <../contracts>` "
"configuration. Odoo pulls from the assigned working schedule, attendance "
"records, planning schedule, and approved time off."
msgstr ""
"Las entradas de trabajo se sincronizan según la configuración "
"del :doc:`contrato <../contracts>` del empleado. Odoo extrae del horario de "
"trabajo asignado, registros de asistencia, horario de planificación y "
"ausencias aprobadas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:640
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:352
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:292
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:346
msgid ""
"Any :ref:`discrepancies or conflicts <payroll/conflicts>` must be resolved, "
"then the work entries can be :ref:`regenerated <payroll/regenerate-work-"
"entries>`."
msgstr ""
"Cualquier :ref:`discrepancia o conflicto <payroll/conflicts>` debe "
"resolverse, luego las entradas de trabajo pueden :ref:`regenerarse <payroll/"
"regenerate-work-entries>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:643
msgid ""
"Once everything is correct, draft payslips can be :ref:`created individually "
"<payroll/process>` or in batches, referred to in the **Payroll** app "
"as :ref:`pay runs <payroll/payroll_localizations/au_run>`."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que todo sea correcto, las nóminas preliminares se "
"pueden :ref:`crear individualmente <payroll/process>` o en lotes, "
"denominados en la aplicación **Nómina** como :ref:`ejecuciones de pago "
"<payroll/payroll_localizations/au_run>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:648
msgid ""
"In Australia, :ref:`individual payslips <payroll/process>` (not part of a "
"pay run) are considered *out-of-cycle* runs. The same payslip rules apply, "
"but the way individual payslips are submitted to the |ATO| in the framework "
"of :abbr:`STP (Single Touch Payroll)` is slightly different."
msgstr ""
"En Australia, las :ref:`nóminas individuales <payroll/process>` (que no "
"forman parte de una ejecución de pago) se consideran ejecuciones *fuera de "
"ciclo*. Se aplican las mismas reglas de nómina, pero la forma en que se "
"envían las nóminas individuales a |ATO| en el marco de :abbr:`STP (Single "
"Touch Payroll)` es ligeramente diferente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:652
msgid ""
"Adding an out-of-cycle payslip to an existing batch is **not** recommended."
msgstr ""
"**No** se recomienda añadir una nómina fuera de ciclo a un lote existente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"The work entries for a pay run, with some time off entered in the work "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Las entradas de trabajo para un período de pago, con algunas ausencias "
"ingresadas en las entradas de trabajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:658
msgid ""
"To reduce payroll processing time, payroll officer typically handle payslips "
"in batches. These batches can be grouped by wage type (e.g., fixed salary or "
"hourly), pay schedule (weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly), department (direct "
"cost or administration), or any other structure that suits the company."
msgstr ""
"Para reducir el tiempo de procesamiento de nóminas, los responsables de "
"nóminas suelen gestionar las nóminas en lotes. Estos lotes se pueden agrupar "
"por tipo de salario (p. ej., salario fijo o por hora), calendario de pago "
"(semanal, quincenal o mensual), departamento (coste directo o "
"administración) o cualquier otra estructura que se adapte a la empresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:666
msgid "Create a pay run"
msgstr "Crear una ejecución de pago"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:668
msgid ""
"First, create a pay run for the desired time period. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Payslips --> Pay Runs` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. Select the desired :guilabel:`Salary "
"Structure`, :guilabel:`Pay Schedule`, and time :guilabel:`Period`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Primero, crea una ejecución de pago para el periodo de tiempo deseado. Ve "
"a :menuselection:`aplicación Nómina --> Nóminas --> Ejecuciones de pago` y "
"haz clic en :guilabel:`Nuevo`. Selecciona la :guilabel:`Estructura "
"Salarial`, el :guilabel:`Calendario de Pago` y el :guilabel:`Periodo` de "
"tiempo deseados, y después haz clic en :guilabel:`Continuar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:672
msgid ""
"Select the employees to create the pay run for, then "
"click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona los empleados para los que crear la ejecución de pago y después "
"haz clic en :guilabel:`Seleccionar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:675
msgid ""
"Employees on a pay run can be filtered by :guilabel:`Salary Structures`."
msgstr ""
"Los empleados en una ejecución de pago se pueden filtrar "
"por :guilabel:`Estructuras Salariales`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:677
msgid ""
":doc:`Work entries <../work_entries>` are directly linked to the time an "
"employee worked. They can be created in the following ways:"
msgstr ""
"Las :doc:`entradas de trabajo <../work_entries>` están directamente "
"vinculadas al tiempo que trabajó un empleado. Se pueden crear de las "
"siguientes formas:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:680
msgid ""
"Automatically, using the employee's :ref:`work schedule <employees/"
"schedule>`."
msgstr ""
"Automáticamente, usando el :ref:`horario de trabajo <employees/schedule>` "
"del empleado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:681
msgid ""
"Automatically, using the :doc:`Attendances app  <../../attendances/"
"attendance_logs>`"
msgstr ""
"Automáticamente, usando la :doc:`aplicación Asistencias  <../../attendances/"
"attendance_logs>`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:682
msgid ""
"Automatically, after publishing :ref:`planned shifts <planning/shifts>`."
msgstr ""
"Automáticamente, después de publicar los :ref:`turnos planificados <planning/"
"shifts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:683
msgid "Manually, via import."
msgstr "Manualmente, mediante importación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:685
msgid ""
"To manually upload work entries, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll App --> "
"Work Entries --> Work Entries`, and view the data in a list. Next, click "
"the :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon and select :guilabel:`Import "
"Records`."
msgstr ""
"Para cargar manualmente entradas de trabajo, ve a :menuselection:`aplicación "
"Nómina --> Entradas de Trabajo --> Entradas de Trabajo` y visualiza los "
"datos en una lista. A continuación, haz clic en el icono :icon:`fa-"
"gear` :guilabel:`(Acciones)` y selecciona :guilabel:`Importar Registros`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:690
msgid ""
"Alternatively, use the built-in **Timesheets** app to record hours. These "
"can then be exported, adjusted slightly (with a few field changes), and re-"
"imported as work entries."
msgstr ""
"Alternativamente, usa la aplicación integrada **Partes de horas** para "
"registrar horas. Estas se pueden exportar, ajustar ligeramente (con algunos "
"cambios de campo) y volver a importar como entradas de trabajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:694
msgid "Currently there is **no** integration with Odoo's **Timesheets** app."
msgstr ""
"Actualmente **no** hay integración con la aplicación **Partes de horas** de "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:697
msgid "Generate payslips"
msgstr "Generar recibos de nómina"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:699
msgid "Payslips can be generated in two ways:"
msgstr "Las nóminas se pueden generar de dos formas:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:701
msgid ""
":ref:`Pay Runs <payroll/payroll_localizations/au_run>`: The recommended "
"method for Australia."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ejecuciones de Pago <payroll/payroll_localizations/au_run>`: El método "
"recomendado para Australia."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:702
msgid ""
"Off-Cycle Payslips: Mainly used for termination payslips, or other payments "
"outside of a pay cycle."
msgstr ""
"Nóminas Fuera de Ciclo: Utilizadas principalmente para nóminas de "
"terminación u otros pagos fuera de un ciclo de pago."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:705
msgid ""
"There is no limit to the amount of payslips that can be created in one pay "
"run."
msgstr ""
"No hay límite en la cantidad de recibos de nómina que se pueden crear en una "
"ejecución de pago."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:707
msgid ""
"After creating a :ref:`pay run <payroll/payroll_localizations/au_run>`, one "
"payslip is created per employee in the Waiting stage, which can be reviewed "
"and amended before validation."
msgstr ""
"Después de crear una :ref:`ejecución de pago <payroll/payroll_localizations/"
"au_run>`, se crea un recibo de nómina por empleado en la etapa En espera, "
"que se puede revisar y modificar antes de la validación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:711
msgid ""
"In the future, payslips that are not related to hours worked should also be "
"handled using off-cycle payslips."
msgstr ""
"En el futuro, los recibos de nómina que no estén relacionados con las horas "
"trabajadas también deberán gestionarse mediante recibos de nómina fuera de "
"ciclo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:715
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payslips.rst:3
msgid "Payslips"
msgstr "Recibos de nómina"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:717
msgid "On the payslip form view, there are two types of inputs:"
msgstr ""
"En la vista de formulario del recibo de nómina, hay dos tipos de entradas:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:719
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Worked days`: Computed based on the work entry source set on the "
"employee's contract. Work entries can be configured according to different "
"types: attendance, overtime, Saturday rate, Sunday rate, public holiday "
"rate, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Días trabajados`: Calculado en función del origen de entrada de "
"trabajo establecido en el contrato del empleado. Las entradas de trabajo se "
"pueden configurar según diferentes tipos: asistencia, horas extra, tarifa de "
"sábado, tarifa de domingo, tarifa de festivo, etc."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:722
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salary inputs`: Individual payments or amounts of different types "
"(allowances, lump sums, deductions, termination payments, leaves, etc.) that "
"have little to do with the hours worked during the current pay period. The "
"previously configured salary attachments are simply recurring other inputs "
"attached to a contract."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Entradas salariales`: Pagos o cantidades individuales de "
"diferentes tipos (asignaciones, sumas globales, deducciones, pagos de "
"terminación, licencias, etc.) que tienen poco que ver con las horas "
"trabajadas durante el período de pago actual. Los embargos salariales "
"configurados previamente son simplemente otras entradas recurrentes "
"vinculadas a un contrato."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:727
msgid ""
"Under the *Salary Computation* tab, Odoo automatically computes payslip "
"rules based on employees, contracts, worked hours and salary input types."
msgstr ""
"En la pestaña *Cálculo salarial*, Odoo calcula automáticamente las reglas "
"del recibo de nómina en función de los empleados, contratos, horas "
"trabajadas y tipos de entrada salarial."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:730
msgid ""
"The salary structure *Australian Employee* has 35 payslip rules that "
"automatically compute and dynamically display according to the payslip "
"inputs."
msgstr ""
"La estructura salarial *Australian Employee* tiene 35 reglas de recibo de "
"nómina que se calculan automáticamente y se muestran dinámicamente según las "
"entradas del recibo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:734
msgid ""
"The following rules apply for the pay period in the accompanying payslip:"
msgstr ""
"Las siguientes reglas se aplican para el período de pago en el recibo de "
"nómina adjunto:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:736
msgid ""
"Basic Salary: The pre-sacrifice gross salary (total contract amount before "
"any deductions)."
msgstr ""
"Salario básico: El salario bruto antes del sacrificio (importe total del "
"contrato antes de cualquier deducción)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:737
msgid ""
"Ordinary Time Earnings: Amount to which the super guarantee percentage needs "
"to be applied"
msgstr ""
"Ingresos por tiempo ordinario: Cantidad a la que se debe aplicar el "
"porcentaje de garantía de superannuation"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:738
msgid "Salary Sacrifice Total: includes the $150 sacrificed to superannuation"
msgstr ""
"Total de sacrificio salarial: incluye los 150 $ sacrificados a la "
"superannuation"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:739
msgid ""
"Taxable Allowance Payments: includes the $10 allowance (cents per KM in this "
"case)"
msgstr ""
"Pagos de asignación imponibles: incluye la asignación de 10 $ (centavos por "
"KM en este caso)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:740
msgid "Taxable Salary: Gross salary amount minus non-taxable amounts"
msgstr ""
"Salario imponible: Importe del salario bruto menos las cantidades no "
"imponibles"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:741
msgid ""
"Salary Withholding and Total Withholding: The total tax amounts to be "
"withheld from the taxable salary and remitted to the ATO."
msgstr ""
"Retención de salario y retención total: Los importes totales de impuestos "
"que se deben retener del salario imponible y remitir a la ATO."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:743
msgid ""
"Net Salary: The \"take-home pay\" or the employee's actual wage after all "
"taxes and deductions."
msgstr ""
"Salario neto: El \"salario neto\" o el salario real del empleado después de "
"todos los impuestos y deducciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:744
msgid ""
"Concessional Super Contribution: In this scenario, the amount sacrificed to "
"superannuation, payable to the employee's super fund in addition to the "
"super guarantee"
msgstr ""
"Contribución de superannuation concesional: En este escenario, la cantidad "
"sacrificada a la superannuation, pagadera al fondo de superannuation del "
"empleado además de la garantía de superannuation"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:746
msgid ""
"Super Guarantee: This is computed as 12% of the ordinary time earnings amount"
msgstr ""
"Garantía de superannuation: Se calcula como el 12% del importe de los "
"ingresos por tiempo ordinario"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:749
msgid "Confirming payslips"
msgstr "Confirmar recibos de nómina"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:751
msgid ""
"Once all payslip data is deemed correct, click :guilabel:`Create Draft "
"Entry` on the pay run. This can also be done payslip by payslip for control "
"reasons."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que todos los datos del recibo de nómina se consideran correctos, "
"haz clic en :guilabel:`Crear asiento borrador` en la ejecución de pago. Esto "
"también se puede hacer recibo por recibo por razones de control."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:754
msgid "This has several impacts:"
msgstr "Esto tiene varios impactos:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:756
msgid "The employee receives their payslip via email + portal accessibility."
msgstr ""
"El empleado recibe su recibo de nómina por correo electrónico + "
"accesibilidad al portal."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:757
msgid "Marking the batch and its payslips as Done."
msgstr "Marcar el lote y sus recibos de nómina como Hecho."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:758
msgid ""
"Creating a draft accounting entry per payslip or one entry for the whole "
"batch, depending on the payroll settings. At this stage, accountants can "
"post entries to affect the balance sheet, P&L report, and BAS report."
msgstr ""
"Creación de un asiento contable en borrador por nómina o un asiento para "
"todo el lote, dependiendo de la configuración de nómina. En esta etapa, los "
"contables pueden publicar asientos para afectar el balance general, el "
"informe de pérdidas y ganancias, y el informe BAS."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:761
msgid ""
"Preparing the |STP| submission (or payroll data to be filed to the ATO as "
"part of |STP| compliance). This needs to be performed by the STP Responsible "
"user, defined under :menuselection:`Payroll --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Preparación del envío de |STP| (o datos de nómina que se presentarán ante el "
"ATO como parte del cumplimiento de |STP|). Esto debe ser realizado por el "
"usuario responsable de STP, definido en :menuselection:`Nómina --> "
"Configuración --> Ajustes`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:764
msgid ""
"Preparing super contribution lines as part of SuperStream compliance. This "
"needs to be done by the HR Super Send user selected "
"under :menuselection:`Payroll --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Preparación de las líneas de contribución de super como parte del "
"cumplimiento de SuperStream. Esto debe ser realizado por el usuario de envío "
"de super de RR.HH. seleccionado en :menuselection:`Nómina --> Configuración "
"--> Ajustes`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:768
msgid "Impact on accounting"
msgstr "Impacto en la contabilidad"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:770
msgid ""
"Four accounts from the Australian :abbr:`CoA (Chart of Accounts)` are "
"included with the payroll localization:"
msgstr ""
"Cuatro cuentas del :abbr:`PdC (Plan de Cuentas)` australiano se incluyen con "
"la localización de nómina:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:773
msgid "`611000 Salaries & Wages`"
msgstr "`611000 Salarios y sueldos`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:774
msgid "`230100 Employee Payroll Taxes`"
msgstr "`230100 Impuestos de nómina del empleado`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:775
msgid "`230200 Employer Payroll Taxes`"
msgstr "`230200 Impuestos de nómina del empleador`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:776
msgid "`230000 Salary Payable`"
msgstr "`230000 Salario por pagar`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:779
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CoA (Chart of Accounts)` configuration is done by default when a "
"company is located in Australia. The account codes and names can be edited "
"to suit the company's needs. If there is no :abbr:`CoA (Chart of Accounts)` "
"account associated with a salary rule (used in a salary structure), Odoo "
"uses the account `Salary Expenses` to create the journal entry, regardless "
"of the nature of the move."
msgstr ""
"La configuración del :abbr:`PdC (Plan de Cuentas)` se realiza por defecto "
"cuando una empresa se encuentra en Australia. Los códigos y nombres de "
"cuenta pueden editarse para adaptarse a las necesidades de la empresa. Si no "
"hay una cuenta de :abbr:`PdC (Plan de Cuentas)` asociada con una regla "
"salarial (utilizada en una estructura salarial), Odoo utiliza la cuenta "
"`Gastos salariales` para crear el asiento contable, independientemente de la "
"naturaleza del movimiento."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:785
msgid ""
"Once payslips are confirmed, a draft journal entry per payslip is created, "
"in the Salaries journal."
msgstr ""
"Una vez confirmadas las nóminas, se crea un asiento contable en borrador por "
"nómina en el diario de salarios."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:787
msgid ""
"The level of detail in a payslip's linked journal entry is determined by how "
"the employee settings are configured and accounts on the salary rules."
msgstr ""
"El nivel de detalle en el asiento contable vinculado de una nómina se "
"determina por cómo están configurados los ajustes del empleado y las cuentas "
"en las reglas salariales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:791
msgid "The following salary rules that impact accounting:"
msgstr "Las siguientes reglas salariales afectan a la contabilidad:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:793
msgid "Fees and Deductions"
msgstr "Comisiones y deducciones"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:794
msgid "Total Withholding"
msgstr "Retención total"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:795
msgid "Child Support Total"
msgstr "Total de manutención infantil"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:796
msgid "Expense Reimbursement"
msgstr "Reembolso de gastos"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:797
msgid "Net Salary"
msgstr "Salario neto"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:798
msgid "Concessional Super Contribution"
msgstr "Contribución de super concesional"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:799
msgid "Super Guarantee"
msgstr "Garantía super"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:801
msgid ""
"Once the journal entry is posted, predefined accounts will impact the "
"company's balance sheet (PAYGW, wages, and superannuation liabilities) and "
"profit & loss report (wages and superannuation expenses). In addition, the "
"employee's gross wage and PAYG withholding will update the BAS report for "
"the relevant period (see Tax Grid: W1 and W2). Accounts can be adjusted to "
"the company's chart of accounts."
msgstr ""
"Una vez publicado el asiento contable, las cuentas predefinidas afectarán el "
"balance general de la empresa (PAYGW, salarios y pasivos de jubilación) y el "
"informe de pérdidas y ganancias (salarios y gastos de jubilación). Además, "
"el salario bruto del empleado y la retención de PAYG actualizarán el informe "
"BAS para el período relevante (consulta la cuadrícula de impuestos: W1 y "
"W2). Las cuentas pueden ajustarse al plan de cuentas de la empresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:808
msgid "Closing the BAS"
msgstr "Cierre del BAS"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:810
msgid "Closing the BAS report now includes payroll sections (W1 to W5)"
msgstr "Cerrar el informe BAS ahora incluye secciones de nómina (W1 a W5)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:812
msgid "Most Common:"
msgstr "Más comunes:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:814
msgid "**W1**: Total salary, wages and other payments"
msgstr "**W1**: Total de salarios, sueldos y otros pagos"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:815
msgid ""
"**W2**: Amounts withheld from salaries or wages and other payments shown at "
"W1"
msgstr ""
"**W2**: Cantidades retenidas de salarios o sueldos y otros pagos mostrados "
"en W1"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:816
msgid "**W5**: Total amounts withheld (W2 + W4 + W3)."
msgstr "**W5**: Total de cantidades retenidas (W2 + W4 + W3)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:818
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:911
msgid "Special cases"
msgstr "Casos especiales"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:820
msgid ""
"**W4**: Amounts withheld where no ABN is quoted (NOT a payroll tax! You can "
"record W4 amounts on vendor bills by using the No ABN tax)"
msgstr ""
"**W4**: Cantidades retenidas cuando no se indica ABN (¡NO es un impuesto de "
"nómina! Puedes registrar las cantidades W4 en facturas de proveedor "
"utilizando el impuesto Sin ABN)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:822
msgid ""
"**W3**: Other amounts withheld (excluding any amount shown at W2 or W4). To "
"use it, select the *Report in W3* checkbox in the employee's record, in the "
"*Payroll* tab."
msgstr ""
"**W3**: Otras cantidades retenidas (excluyendo cualquier cantidad mostrada "
"en W2 o W4). Para utilizarla, marca la casilla *Informar en W3* en el "
"registro del empleado, en la pestaña *Nómina*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:826
msgid ""
"For Consolidated payroll accounting entries, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"enable :guilabel:`Batch Account Move Lines`."
msgstr ""
"Para entradas contables consolidadas de nómina, ve a :menuselection:`Nómina "
"--> Configuración --> Ajustes` y activa :guilabel:`Agrupar líneas de asiento "
"contable`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:830
msgid "Submit STP files to the ATO"
msgstr "Enviar archivos STP a la ATO"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:832
msgid ""
"As per |ATO| requirements, |STP| submissions for a pay run **must** be done "
"*on or before* the payday. For this reason, submit |STP| data to the |ATO| "
"**before** proceeding with payment. To submit the data, "
"click :guilabel:`Submit to ATO` on the payslip or pay run."
msgstr ""
"Según los requisitos de |ATO|, los envíos de |STP| para una nómina **deben** "
"realizarse *en o antes* del día de pago. Por esta razón, envía los datos de |"
"STP| a la |ATO| **antes** de proceder con el pago. Para enviar los datos, "
"haz clic en :guilabel:`Enviar a ATO` en la nómina o ejecución de nómina."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:837
msgid "A warning message appears if important information is missing."
msgstr "Aparece un mensaje de advertencia si falta información importante."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:839
msgid ""
"On the |STP| record for the pay run, a few useful information is displayed:"
msgstr ""
"En el registro de |STP| para la ejecución de nómina, se muestra información "
"útil:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:841
msgid "A warning message if important information is missing."
msgstr "Un mensaje de advertencia si falta información importante."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:842
msgid "An automatically generated activity for the |STP| responsible user."
msgstr ""
"Una actividad generada automáticamente para el usuario responsable de |STP|."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:843
msgid ""
"A summary of payslips contained in this pay run, auditable from this view."
msgstr ""
"Un resumen de las nóminas contenidas en esta ejecución de nómina, auditable "
"desde esta vista."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:845
msgid "Always test the submission before submitting."
msgstr "Prueba siempre el envío antes de enviarlo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:847
msgid ""
"Once the |STP| record is ready, click :guilabel:`Submit to ATO`, then read "
"and accept the related terms and conditions."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que el registro de |STP| esté listo, haz clic en :guilabel:`Enviar a "
"ATO` y luego lee y acepta los términos y condiciones relacionados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:None
msgid "Example of an STP record."
msgstr "Ejemplo de un registro STP."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:854
msgid "Pay, refund, and print payslips"
msgstr "Pagar, reembolsar e imprimir nóminas"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:856
msgid "When payslips are submitted to |ATO| you will see 2 options:"
msgstr "Cuando las nóminas se envían a |ATO|, verás 2 opciones:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:858
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mark as Paid`: Click this if you are not using Odoo for "
"accounting (this serves as an internal note that the pay run was paid)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Marcar como Pagado`: Haz clic aquí si no usas Odoo para "
"contabilidad (esto sirve como nota interna de que la nómina fue pagada)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:860
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paid`: Click this if you want to generate a payment file for "
"later reconciliation. Here, you can also select :guilabel:`ABA Credit "
"Transfer` as the payment method. The ABA file can be downloaded directly "
"from the pay run."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pagado`: Haz clic aquí si quieres generar un archivo de pago para "
"reconciliación posterior. Aquí también puedes "
"seleccionar :guilabel:`Transferencia de Crédito ABA` como método de pago. El "
"archivo ABA se puede descargar directamente desde la nómina."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:865
msgid ":ref:`ABA files for batch payments <australia/aba>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Archivos ABA para pagos por lotes <australia/aba>`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:866
msgid ":ref:`How to pay, refund and print payslips <payroll/new-payslip>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Cómo pagar, reembolsar e imprimir nóminas <payroll/new-payslip>`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:869
msgid "Super contributions"
msgstr "Contribuciones de super"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:871
msgid ""
"Superannuation payments to employees' super funds must be processed at least "
"once per quarter, or more frequently when preparing for Payday Super."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos de superanualización a los fondos de super de los empleados deben "
"procesarse al menos una vez por trimestre, o con mayor frecuencia al "
"prepararse para Payday Super."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:874
msgid "There are two ways to access Super Contribution records:"
msgstr "Hay dos formas de acceder a los registros de Contribución de Super:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:876
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --> Super "
"Contributions`."
msgstr ""
"Ve a :menuselection:`aplicación Nómina --> Informes --> Contribuciones de "
"Super`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:877
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cash` :guilabel:`Super Contribution` smart button on the "
"individual payslip."
msgstr ""
"Haz clic en el botón inteligente :icon:`fa-cash` :guilabel:`Contribución de "
"Super` en la nómina individual."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:879
msgid "Super Record Information includes:"
msgstr "La información del Registro de Super incluye:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:881
msgid "Bank Information (used for direct debit processing)"
msgstr "Información Bancaria (usada para procesamiento de débito directo)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:882
msgid "Payslip Lines associated with the contributions"
msgstr "Líneas de Nómina asociadas con las contribuciones"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:883
msgid "Contribution Amounts for each employee"
msgstr "Montos de Contribución para cada empleado"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:884
msgid "Reporting Status"
msgstr "Estado del Informe"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:885
msgid "Direct Debit Status"
msgstr "Estado del Débito Directo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:886
msgid "Fund Update Banner (to highlight any required updates or issues)"
msgstr ""
"Banner de Actualización del Fondo (para resaltar actualizaciones o problemas "
"requeridos)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:889
msgid "Paying super"
msgstr "Pagar super"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:891
msgid ""
"Lock the super record. Navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting "
"--> Super Contributions` and lock the record. Once locked, further "
"contributions create a new super record, just like replenishing new products "
"in the **Purchasing** app create a new RFQ."
msgstr ""
"Bloquea el registro de super. Ve a :menuselection:`aplicación Nómina --> "
"Informes --> Contribuciones de Super` y bloquea el registro. Una vez "
"bloqueado, las contribuciones adicionales crean un nuevo registro de super, "
"igual que reponer nuevos productos en la aplicación **Compras** crea una "
"nueva SdC."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:894
msgid ""
"Register the super payment. This will create a payment record in Odoo, and "
"authorise the clearing house to collect the contributions via direct debit."
msgstr ""
"Registra el pago de super. Esto creará un registro de pago en Odoo y "
"autorizará a la cámara de compensación a cobrar las contribuciones mediante "
"débito directo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:896
msgid "Wait for the following statuses to update:"
msgstr "Espera a que se actualicen los siguientes estados:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:898
msgid ""
"Direct debit status (payment status from the employer to the clearing house)"
msgstr ""
"Estado del débito directo (estado del pago del empleador a la cámara de "
"compensación)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:899
msgid ""
"Fund payment status (payment status from the clearing house to the super "
"funds)"
msgstr ""
"Estado del pago del fondo (estado del pago de la cámara de compensación a "
"los fondos de jubilación)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:900
msgid "Payment status (payment status of the entire transaction)"
msgstr "Estado del pago (estado del pago de toda la transacción)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:902
msgid "Reconcile. You can now reconcile the payment with the bank statement."
msgstr "Concilia. Ahora puedes conciliar el pago con el extracto bancario."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:905
msgid ""
"As of July 1, 2026, Australian businesses will be **required** to pay super "
"at the same time as salary & wages. This Governmental initiative is called "
"*Payday Super*. Find more information on the `ATO website <https://"
"www.ato.gov.au/businesses-and-organisations/super-for-employers/payday-"
"super>`_ ."
msgstr ""
"A partir del 1 de julio de 2026, las empresas australianas estarán "
"**obligadas** a pagar la jubilación al mismo tiempo que los salarios. Esta "
"iniciativa gubernamental se llama *Payday Super*. Encuentra más información "
"en el `sitio web de ATO <https://www.ato.gov.au/businesses-and-organisations/"
"super-for-employers/payday-super>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:913
msgid "The following are common situations and their resolutions:"
msgstr "Las siguientes son situaciones comunes y sus resoluciones:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:915
msgid "*What if I need to cancel my super payment?*"
msgstr "*¿Qué pasa si necesito cancelar mi pago de jubilación?*"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:917
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --> Super "
"Contributions`. Find the entry to cancel and click :guilabel:`Cancel`. The "
"chatter log will display information regarding the *Direct Debit Status*, "
"identifying whether it is a cancellation or a refund."
msgstr ""
"Navega a :menuselection:`aplicación Nómina --> Informes --> Contribuciones "
"de jubilación`. Encuentra la entrada a cancelar y haz clic "
"en :guilabel:`Cancelar`. El registro de conversación mostrará información "
"sobre el *Estado del débito directo*, identificando si es una cancelación o "
"un reembolso."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:921
msgid "*What if my direct debit payment fails?*"
msgstr "*¿Qué pasa si falla mi pago por débito directo?*"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:923
msgid ""
"On the Super record, the *Direct Debit Status* will be marked as *Failed*. "
"Either resubmit or cancel the super transaction"
msgstr ""
"En el registro de jubilación, el *Estado del débito directo* se marcará como "
"*Fallido*. Vuelve a enviar o cancela la transacción de jubilación"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:926
msgid "*What if one of the fund payment fails?*"
msgstr "*¿Qué pasa si falla uno de los pagos del fondo?*"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:928
msgid ""
"On the Super record lines, the *Fund Payment Status* will be marked as "
"*Failed*. Either resubmit or cancel the super transaction."
msgstr ""
"En las líneas del registro de jubilación, el *Estado del pago del fondo* se "
"marcará como *Fallido*. Vuelve a enviar o cancela la transacción de "
"jubilación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:932
msgid "Payroll links to other apps"
msgstr "Enlaces de nómina a otras aplicaciones"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:934
msgid ""
"The following apps integrate with the **Payroll** app, and require specific "
"configurations or considerations."
msgstr ""
"Las siguientes aplicaciones se integran con la aplicación **Nómina** y "
"requieren configuraciones o consideraciones específicas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:938
msgid "Time Off"
msgstr "Ausencias"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:940
msgid ""
"Logging time off of any kind replaces the employee's work entries. This "
"takes place because time off types are linked to work entry types."
msgstr ""
"Registrar cualquier tipo de ausencia reemplaza las entradas de trabajo del "
"empleado. Esto ocurre porque los tipos de ausencias están vinculados a los "
"tipos de entradas de trabajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:943
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Time Off app --> Configuration --> Time Off "
"Types`. For each type, configure the following two fields under the "
"*Payroll* section:"
msgstr ""
"Navega a :menuselection:`aplicación Ausencias --> Configuración --> Tipos de "
"ausencias`. Para cada tipo, configura los siguientes dos campos en la "
"sección *Nómina*:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:946
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Type`: Defines which work entry is selected on the "
"*Worked Days* table of the payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipo de entrada de trabajo`: Define qué entrada de trabajo se "
"selecciona en la tabla *Días trabajados* de la nómina."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:948
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unused Leave Type`: Choose between :guilabel:`General "
"Leave`, :guilabel:`Long Service`, or :guilabel:`Unpaid at Termination`. "
"If :guilabel:`Unpaid at Termination` is selected, the remaining leave "
"balance for this time off type will not show up as an entitlement at the "
"time of termination."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipo de permiso no utilizado`: Elige entre :guilabel:`Permiso "
"general`, :guilabel:`Servicio prolongado` o :guilabel:`Sin remuneración al "
"terminar`. Si se selecciona :guilabel:`Sin remuneración al terminar`, el "
"saldo de permisos restante para este tipo de ausencia no aparecerá como un "
"derecho en el momento de la terminación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:954
msgid "Expenses"
msgstr "Gastos"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:957
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"enable the option"
msgstr ""
"Navega a :menuselection:`aplicación Gastos --> Configuración --> Ajustes` y "
"activa la opción"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:957
msgid ":guilabel:`Reimburse in Payslip`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Reembolsar en nómina`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:959
msgid ""
"When an employee on the payroll submits an approved expense to be "
"reimbursed, it can be reimbursed in two ways:"
msgstr ""
"Cuando un empleado en la nómina envía un gasto aprobado para ser "
"reembolsado, puede reembolsarse de dos formas:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:962
msgid ""
"If the expense is to be reimbursed *outside* of a pay run, "
"click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`. The payment must be made manually."
msgstr ""
"Si el gasto debe reembolsarse *fuera* de una nómina, haz clic "
"en :guilabel:`Publicar asientos contables`. El pago debe hacerse manualmente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:964
msgid ""
"If the expense is to be reimbursed as part of the next *pay run*, "
"click :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` instead."
msgstr ""
"Si el gasto debe reembolsarse como parte de la siguiente *nómina*, haz clic "
"en :guilabel:`Reportar en la siguiente nómina`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:967
msgid ""
"The expense will be visible under *Payslip Salary Inputs*, *Salary "
"Computation*, and the printed payslip."
msgstr ""
"El gasto será visible en *Entradas salariales de nómina*, *Cálculo salarial* "
"y la nómina impresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:975
msgid ""
"On the employee's record, set the :guilabel:`Work Entry Source` field "
"to :guilabel:`Attendances`."
msgstr ""
"En el registro del empleado, establece el campo :guilabel:`Origen de entrada "
"de trabajo` en :guilabel:`Asistencias`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:977
msgid ""
"Work entries will be created as soon as the employee signs in and out via "
"the **Attendances** app."
msgstr ""
"Las entradas de trabajo se crearán tan pronto como el empleado fiche entrada "
"y salida a través de la aplicación **Asistencias**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:979
msgid ""
"On the payslip, only the actual time worked will be displayed in the worked "
"days and hours table."
msgstr ""
"En la nómina, solo se mostrará el tiempo realmente trabajado en la tabla de "
"días y horas trabajadas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:986
msgid ""
"On the employee's record, set the :guilabel:`Work Entry Source` field "
"to :guilabel:`Planning`."
msgstr ""
"En el registro del empleado, establece el campo :guilabel:`Origen de entrada "
"de trabajo` en :guilabel:`Planificación`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:988
msgid "Work entries will be created as soon as planning shifts are published."
msgstr ""
"Las entradas de trabajo se crearán tan pronto como se publiquen los turnos "
"de planificación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:990
msgid "On the payslip, only time worked will show in the worked days table."
msgstr ""
"En la nómina, solo se mostrará el tiempo trabajado en la tabla de días "
"trabajados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:993
msgid "Casual workers"
msgstr "Trabajadores ocasionales"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:995
msgid "*Casual employment* is specific to Australia and New Zealand."
msgstr "El *empleo ocasional* es específico de Australia y Nueva Zelanda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:997
msgid ""
"An employee is considered casual if, at the time they commence employment, "
"one of the following applies:"
msgstr ""
"Un empleado se considera ocasional si, en el momento en que comienza el "
"empleo, se aplica una de las siguientes condiciones:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1001
msgid "No firm commitment"
msgstr "Sin compromiso firme"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1003
msgid ""
"There is no firm advance commitment to ongoing and indefinite work, taking "
"into account various relevant factors; and work schedules cannot be reliably "
"used for casual employees in Odoo due to the absence of a fixed or ongoing "
"commitment to work."
msgstr ""
"No existe un compromiso firme anticipado de trabajo continuo e indefinido, "
"teniendo en cuenta varios factores relevantes; y los horarios de trabajo no "
"pueden utilizarse de manera fiable para empleados ocasionales en Odoo debido "
"a la ausencia de un compromiso fijo o continuo de trabajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1007
msgid ""
"Instead, it is recommended to use the **Planning** or **Attendances** apps "
"to record actual work entries."
msgstr ""
"En su lugar, se recomienda usar las aplicaciones **Planificación** o "
"**Asistencias** para registrar las entradas de trabajo reales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1011
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Working Hours` field on an employee record can be left empty "
"for casual employees."
msgstr ""
"El campo :guilabel:`Horario de trabajo` en el registro de un empleado puede "
"dejarse vacío para empleados ocasionales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1014
msgid "Entitled to casual loading"
msgstr "Con derecho a recargo ocasional"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1016
msgid ""
"They are entitled to receive a casual loading or a specific casual pay rate "
"under an award, registered agreement, or employment contract."
msgstr ""
"Tienen derecho a recibir un recargo ocasional o una tarifa específica de "
"pago ocasional según un laudo, acuerdo registrado o contrato de empleo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1019
msgid ""
"A casual loading rate can be applied to employees who are paid on an hourly "
"basis, rather than a fixed wage, which is intended for full-time or part-"
"time staff."
msgstr ""
"Se puede aplicar una tarifa de recargo ocasional a los empleados que reciben "
"pago por hora, en lugar de un salario fijo, que está destinado al personal a "
"tiempo completo o parcial."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1023
msgid "Penalty rates"
msgstr "Tarifas de penalización"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1025
msgid ""
"In addition to casual loading, Odoo allows you to apply penalty rates based "
"on the timing of a shift (e.g., Saturdays, Sundays, Public Holidays)."
msgstr ""
"Además de la carga ocasional, Odoo te permite aplicar tasas de penalización "
"basadas en el horario de un turno (p. ej., sábados, domingos, días festivos)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1028
msgid ""
"To implement this, :ref:`create a separate work entry type <payroll/new-work-"
"entry-type>` for each penalty category."
msgstr ""
"Para implementar esto, :ref:`crea un tipo de entrada de trabajo "
"independiente <payroll/new-work-entry-type>` para cada categoría de "
"penalización."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1032
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/egypt.rst:217
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:263
msgid "Overtime"
msgstr "Horas extraordinarias"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1034
msgid ""
"Using the same field as for penalty rates, you can apply an additional "
"percentage for overtime hours."
msgstr ""
"Usando el mismo campo que para las tasas de penalización, puedes aplicar un "
"porcentaje adicional para las horas extra."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1037
msgid ""
"For each overtime type, :ref:`create a separate work entry type <payroll/new-"
"work-entry-type>`. Unlike penalties, overtime is different because casual "
"loading does not apply to overtime hours."
msgstr ""
"Para cada tipo de horas extra, :ref:`crea un tipo de entrada de trabajo "
"independiente <payroll/new-work-entry-type>`. A diferencia de las "
"penalizaciones, las horas extra son diferentes porque la carga ocasional no "
"se aplica a las horas extra."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1041
msgid "Managing casual worker rates"
msgstr "Gestión de tasas de trabajadores ocasionales"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1043
msgid ""
"Configure all work entry types with the appropriate *penalty* and *overtime* "
"rates."
msgstr ""
"Configura todos los tipos de entrada de trabajo con las tasas de "
"*penalización* y *horas extra* apropiadas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1044
msgid ""
"Record work entries using the :ref:`Attendances <payroll/"
"payroll_localizations/attn_au>` or :ref:`Planning <payroll/"
"payroll_localizations/plan_au>` apps."
msgstr ""
"Registra las entradas de trabajo usando las aplicaciones :ref:`Asistencias "
"<payroll/payroll_localizations/attn_au>` o :ref:`Planificación <payroll/"
"payroll_localizations/plan_au>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1046
msgid ""
"Manually update work entries daily or weekly in the **Attendance** app, "
"assigning them to the correct work entry type."
msgstr ""
"Actualiza manualmente las entradas de trabajo diaria o semanalmente en la "
"aplicación **Asistencias**, asignándolas al tipo de entrada de trabajo "
"correcto."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1048
msgid ""
"If manual updates are not suitable, a practical alternative is to import "
"work entries from a spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Si las actualizaciones manuales no son adecuadas, una alternativa práctica "
"es importar las entradas de trabajo desde una hoja de cálculo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1051
msgid ""
"You can view this information on the employee's payslip. There are two "
"active smart buttons that allow for quick access to work entries, to make "
"adjustments and attendance records as well."
msgstr ""
"Puedes ver esta información en la nómina del empleado. Hay dos botones "
"inteligentes activos que permiten un acceso rápido a las entradas de trabajo "
"para realizar ajustes y registros de asistencia también."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1057
msgid "Terminate employees"
msgstr "Dar de baja empleados"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1059
msgid ""
"Employees can be terminated by going to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Reporting --> Terminate Employee`. The following fields must be completed:"
msgstr ""
"Los empleados pueden ser dados de baja yendo a :menuselection:`aplicación "
"Nómina --> Informes --> Dar de baja empleado`. Los siguientes campos deben "
"completarse:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1062
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract End Date`: Once the termination is validated, this date "
"is added to the contract automatically, and marks the contract as *Expired* "
"when the date has been reached."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fecha de finalización del contrato`: Una vez validada la baja, "
"esta fecha se añade automáticamente al contrato y marca el contrato como "
"*Caducado* cuando se alcanza la fecha."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1064
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cessation Type Code`: A mandatory field for the ATO's STP "
"reporting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Código de tipo de cese`: Un campo obligatorio para el informe STP "
"de la ATO."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1065
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Termination Type`: The type of redundancy (genuine or non-"
"genuine) affects the computation of unused annual and long service leave "
"withholding."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipo de baja`: El tipo de despido (genuino o no genuino) afecta "
"al cálculo de las vacaciones anuales no utilizadas y la retención de "
"licencia por servicio prolongado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1068
msgid ""
"The Final payslip will be marked as final pay. Besides normal wages & "
"benefits, it will contain unused leaves, auto-calculated by Odoo."
msgstr ""
"La nómina final se marcará como pago final. Además de los salarios y "
"beneficios normales, contendrá las vacaciones no utilizadas, calculadas "
"automáticamente por Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1071
msgid ""
"On top of these payments, you can add ETPs. These can be of 2 types: "
"Excluded ETPs & Non-excluded ETPs. These are simply taxed differently, and "
"cover different types of employment scenarios. They also depend on the type "
"of redundancy. Find more information on the `ATO website <https://"
"www.ato.gov.au/businesses-and-organisations/super-for-employers/payday-"
"super>`_ ."
msgstr ""
"Además de estos pagos, puedes añadir ETPs. Estos pueden ser de 2 tipos: ETPs "
"excluidos y ETPs no excluidos. Simplemente se gravan de manera diferente y "
"cubren diferentes tipos de escenarios laborales. También dependen del tipo "
"de despido. Encuentra más información en el `sitio web de ATO <https://"
"www.ato.gov.au/businesses-and-organisations/super-for-employers/payday-"
"super>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1077
msgid ""
"Annual leaves will be taxed as per |ATO| schedule 7. ETPs will be taxed as "
"per |ATO| schedule 11."
msgstr ""
"Las vacaciones anuales se gravarán según el |ATO| anexo 7. Los ETPs se "
"gravarán según el |ATO| anexo 11."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1080
msgid "Advanced configurations"
msgstr "Configuraciones avanzadas"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1082
msgid ""
"In some cases, if there is a need to add more inputs to an employee's salary "
"that are not covered by the default input type, other input types can be "
"configured or created."
msgstr ""
"En algunos casos, si es necesario añadir más entradas al salario de un "
"empleado que no estén cubiertas por el tipo de entrada predeterminado, se "
"pueden configurar o crear otros tipos de entrada."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1086
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:438
msgid "Other input types"
msgstr "Otros tipos de entrada"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1088
msgid ""
"To edit or create another input types, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll --"
"> Configuration --> Other Input Types`. To modify an existing type, click on "
"the rule and make the desired changes. To create a new input type, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, then fill out the :guilabel:`Payslip Other Input "
"Types` form."
msgstr ""
"Para editar o crear otros tipos de entrada, navega a :menuselection:`Nómina "
"--> Configuración --> Otros tipos de entrada`. Para modificar un tipo "
"existente, haz clic en la regla y realiza los cambios deseados. Para crear "
"un nuevo tipo de entrada, haz clic en :guilabel:`Nuevo`, luego completa el "
"formulario :guilabel:`Otros tipos de entrada de nómina`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1094
msgid ""
"A total of sixty-three other input types are related to the Australia "
"payroll localization. It is **not** recommended to use these other input "
"types, since they **cannot** be used in the frame of |STP|. These can be "
"archived or deleted."
msgstr ""
"Un total de sesenta y tres tipos de entrada adicionales están relacionados "
"con la localización de nómina de Australia. **No** se recomienda usar estos "
"otros tipos de entrada, ya que **no pueden** usarse en el marco de |STP|. "
"Estos pueden archivarse o eliminarse."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1098
msgid ""
"On each input type being used, ensure the following fields are populated:"
msgstr ""
"En cada tipo de entrada que se use, asegúrate de que los siguientes campos "
"estén completos:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Type`: Select the classification for the input types "
"using the drop-down menu. The default options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipo de pago`: Selecciona la clasificación para los tipos de "
"entrada usando el menú desplegable. Las opciones predeterminadas son:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1103
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ETP`: The input is an :abbr:`ETP (Employment Termination "
"Payments)`. These are either considered excluded or non-excluded. Refer to "
"the |ATO| web page on :abbr:`ETP (Employment Termination Payments)` "
"components taxation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ETP`: La entrada es un :abbr:`ETP (Pagos por Terminación de "
"Empleo)`. Estos se consideran excluidos o no excluidos. Consulta la página "
"web de |ATO| sobre tributación de componentes de :abbr:`ETP (Pagos por "
"Terminación de Empleo)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allowance`: The input is a separate amount paid to employees in "
"addition to their salary and wages. Some of these allowances are mandated by "
"modern awards, such as laundry, transportation, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Asignación`: La entrada es un importe separado pagado a los "
"empleados además de su salario. Algunas de estas asignaciones son "
"obligatorias según normas modernas, como lavandería, transporte, etc."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1111
msgid ""
"Contact Odoo if planning to use allowances subject to varied rates of "
"withholding (such as cents per kilometer or travel allowances) to ensure "
"Odoo currently covers the particular business case."
msgstr ""
"Contacta con Odoo si planeas usar asignaciones sujetas a tasas variables de "
"retención (como céntimos por kilómetro o asignaciones de viaje) para "
"asegurar que Odoo cubra actualmente el caso de negocio particular."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1116
msgid ""
"As of Odoo 18, some allowances, such as :guilabel:`Laundry`, which is used "
"for approved uniforms, are managed by two other inputs: one to lodge the "
"amount paid up to the |ATO| limit, and the other one to lodge the amount "
"exceeding the ATO limit. This is necessary for Odoo to compute PAYGW "
"correctly. Some businesses may require to shift the reporting of an "
"allowance from OTE to Salary & Wages depending on the employee. In this "
"case, the input type must be duplicated and reconfigured from an existing "
"other input type. For example, :guilabel:`Work-Related Non-Expense: "
"Allowance to compensate for specific work, activities, disabilities, skills "
"or qualifications` is OTE by default."
msgstr ""
"A partir de Odoo 18, algunas asignaciones, como :guilabel:`Lavandería`, que "
"se usa para uniformes aprobados, se gestionan mediante otras dos entradas: "
"una para registrar el importe pagado hasta el límite de |ATO|, y otra para "
"registrar el importe que excede el límite ATO. Esto es necesario para que "
"Odoo calcule PAYGW correctamente. Algunas empresas pueden necesitar cambiar "
"el reporte de una asignación de OTE a Salario según el empleado. En este "
"caso, el tipo de entrada debe duplicarse y reconfigurarse a partir de un "
"tipo de entrada existente. Por ejemplo, :guilabel:`Relacionado con el "
"trabajo no reembolsable: Asignación para compensar trabajo específico, "
"actividades, discapacidades, habilidades o cualificaciones` es OTE por "
"defecto."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1125
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Deduction`: The input is a deduction such as union fees and child "
"support."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Deducción`: La entrada es una deducción como cuotas sindicales y "
"manutención infantil."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Leave`: The input is a leave-related other input that does not "
"pertain to a single pay period (lump sum, cashing out leaves while in "
"service, unused leaves, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Permiso`: La entrada es otra entrada relacionada con permisos que "
"no pertenece a un único período de pago (suma global, cobro de permisos "
"mientras se está en servicio, permisos no usados, etc.)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Lump Sum`: This input is a return to work and lump sums (for back "
"payments)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Suma global`: Esta entrada es un retorno al trabajo y sumas "
"globales (para pagos atrasados)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Other`: The input is another payment with its own specific logic."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Otro`: La entrada es otro pago con su propia lógica específica."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PAYGW Treatment`: This field affects how Odoo withholds tax for "
"the input type. Using the drop-down menu, select "
"either: :guilabel:`Regular`, :guilabel:`No PAYG Withholding`, "
"or :guilabel:`Taxed above ATO limit`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tratamiento PAYGW`: Este campo afecta cómo Odoo retiene impuestos "
"para el tipo de entrada. Usando el menú desplegable, "
"selecciona: :guilabel:`Regular`, :guilabel:`Sin retención PAYG`, "
"o :guilabel:`Gravado por encima del límite ATO`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Superannuation Treatment`: Using the drop-down menu, select if "
"the input is considered a :guilabel:`OTE` (one-time "
"earning), :guilabel:`Salary & Wages`, or :guilabel:`Not Salary & Wages`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tratamiento de jubilación`: Usando el menú desplegable, "
"selecciona si la entrada se considera :guilabel:`OTE` (ganancia "
"única), :guilabel:`Salario`, o :guilabel:`No salario`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`STP Code`: This field is only visible in developer mode. This "
"field tells Odoo how to report the gross value of the payment to the |ATO|. "
"It is **not** recommended to change the value of this field if it is already "
"populated by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Código STP`: Este campo solo es visible en modo desarrollador. "
"Este campo indica a Odoo cómo reportar el valor bruto del pago a |ATO|. "
"**No** se recomienda cambiar el valor de este campo si ya está completo por "
"defecto."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is OTE`: This field determines whether time spent in this "
"category can be considered ordinary time earnings, meaning that the "
"superannuation guarantee rate will apply (e.g., regular attendance, paid "
"leave, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Es OTE`: Este campo determina si el tiempo dedicado a esta "
"categoría puede considerarse ganancias de tiempo ordinario, lo que significa "
"que se aplicará la tasa de garantía de jubilación (p. ej., asistencia "
"regular, permiso pagado, etc.)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Penalty Rate`: This field is used to determine the percentage of "
"penalty that applies to time spent in this category. It is important to "
"configure the penalty rate that applies in the state or industry according "
"to the type of work (e.g., Saturday rate, Sunday rate, overtime rate, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tasa de penalización`: Este campo se usa para determinar el "
"porcentaje de penalización que se aplica al tiempo dedicado a esta "
"categoría. Es importante configurar la tasa de penalización que se aplica en "
"el estado o la industria según el tipo de trabajo (p. ej., tasa de sábado, "
"tasa de domingo, tasa de horas extra, etc.)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1149
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:451
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:506
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:537
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:398
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:418
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:539
msgid "Close Payroll"
msgstr "Cerrar nómina"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1151
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:453
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:508
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:539
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:400
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:420
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:541
msgid "If there are no errors, payroll is completed for the pay period."
msgstr "Si no hay errores, la nómina se completa para el período de pago."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1154
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:511
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/kenya.rst:152
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:544
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Informes"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1156
msgid ""
"The Australian localization contains several reports unique to Australia, "
"which provide information on superfund contributions, single touch "
"payroll, :abbr:`STP (Single Touch Payroll)` Finalisation, and the ability to "
"terminate employees."
msgstr ""
"La localización australiana contiene varios informes exclusivos de "
"Australia, que proporcionan información sobre contribuciones a superfondos, "
"nómina de toque único, :abbr:`STP (Nómina de Toque Único)` Finalización, y "
"la capacidad de dar de baja empleados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1161
msgid "STP Finalisation"
msgstr "Finalización STP"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1163
msgid ""
"The fiscal year in Australia ends on June 30th, but :abbr:`STP (Single Touch "
"Payroll)` finalisation declarations are due by July 14th. These can be done "
"in :ref:`one single report for all employees <payroll/stp-total>`, "
"or :ref:`individually <payroll/stp-individual>`."
msgstr ""
"El año fiscal en Australia termina el 30 de junio, pero las declaraciones de "
"finalización de :abbr:`STP (Nómina de Toque Único)` vencen el 14 de julio. "
"Estas pueden hacerse en :ref:`un único informe para todos los empleados "
"<payroll/stp-total>`, o :ref:`individualmente <payroll/stp-individual>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1170
msgid "EOFY finalisation"
msgstr "Finalización EOFY"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1172
msgid ""
"To finalize the fiscal year's :abbr:`STP (Single Touch Payroll)`, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --> STP Finalisation`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Finalise Payroll` pop-up window loads."
msgstr ""
"Para finalizar el :abbr:`STP (Nómina de Toque Único)` del año fiscal, navega "
"a :menuselection:`aplicación Nómina --> Informes --> Finalización STP`, y se "
"carga una ventana emergente :guilabel:`Finalizar nómina`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1176
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Company`, :guilabel:`ABN`, and :guilabel:`Branch Code` are "
"populated from the :ref:`company information <payroll/payroll_localizations/"
"au_gen>`."
msgstr ""
"Los campos :guilabel:`Empresa`, :guilabel:`ABN` y :guilabel:`Código de "
"sucursal` se rellenan desde la :ref:`información de la empresa <payroll/"
"payroll_localizations/au_gen>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1179
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:431
#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/allocations.rst:186
msgid "Configure the following fields on the form:"
msgstr "Configura los siguientes campos en el formulario:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1181
msgid ""
":guilabel:`BMS ID`: Enter the company's :abbr:`BMS ID (Business Management "
"Software Identifier)`, issued by the |ATO|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID de BMS`: introduce el :abbr:`ID de BMS (identificador de "
"software de gestión empresarial)` de la empresa, emitido por la |ATO|."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`EOFY Declaration`: Select this checkbox to indicate the "
"finalisation is for the entire fiscal year (not an :ref:`individual "
"finalisation <payroll/stp-individual>`). Once selected, the name of the "
"report changes to `EOFY Finalisation - YYYY/YY`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Declaración de EOFY`: marca esta casilla para indicar que la "
"finalización es para todo el ejercicio fiscal (no una :ref:`finalización "
"individual <payroll/stp-individual>`). Una vez seleccionada, el nombre del "
"informe cambia a `Finalización de EOFY - AAAA/AA`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1186
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Finalisation`: Select this checkbox to indicate this is a "
"finalisation and not an amendment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Finalización`: marca esta casilla para indicar que se trata de "
"una finalización y no de una modificación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1188
msgid ":guilabel:`Date Start`: This field displays `1 July`, by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fecha de inicio`: este campo muestra `1 de julio` de forma "
"predeterminada."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1189
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Date End`: If :guilabel:`EOFY Declaration` is selected, this "
"field displays `30 June YYYY`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fecha de fin`: si se selecciona :guilabel:`Declaración de EOFY`, "
"este campo muestra `30 de junio de AAAA`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1191
msgid ":guilabel:`Fiscal Year`: The current fiscal year populates this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ejercicio fiscal`: el ejercicio fiscal actual rellena este campo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1192
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Responsible User`: Using the drop-down menu, select the user "
"responsible for this report."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Usuario responsable`: con el menú desplegable, selecciona el "
"usuario responsable de este informe."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:None
msgid "EOFY finalisation top half filled out."
msgstr "Mitad superior de la finalización de EOFY rellenada."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1198
msgid ""
"Both active and :ref:`terminated <payroll/au-terminate>` employees to "
"finalise are displayed in the :guilabel:`Employee Finalisation` tab. Ensure "
"all balances for all employees are correct. Once verified, "
"click :guilabel:`Submit to ATO` to create the report and submit it."
msgstr ""
"Tanto los empleados activos como los :ref:`dados de baja <payroll/au-"
"terminate>` que deben finalizarse se muestran en la "
"pestaña :guilabel:`Finalización del empleado`. Asegúrate de que todos los "
"saldos de todos los empleados sean correctos. Una vez verificado, haz clic "
"en :guilabel:`Enviar a ATO` para crear el informe y enviarlo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1202
msgid ""
"Employee payment information changes to *Tax ready* on their online income "
"statement, after the end of the financial year."
msgstr ""
"La información de pago del empleado cambia a *Listo para impuestos* en su "
"declaración de ingresos en línea, después del final del ejercicio fiscal."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1208
msgid "Individual finalisation"
msgstr "Finalización individual"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1210
msgid ""
"Employees can be individually finalised during the year. This can be useful "
"when:"
msgstr ""
"Los empleados se pueden finalizar individualmente durante el año. Esto puede "
"ser útil cuando:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1212
msgid ""
"A one-off (off-cycle) payment is made *after* a finalisation is sent to "
"the :abbr:`ATO (Australian Taxation Office)`."
msgstr ""
"Se realiza un pago único (fuera de ciclo) *después* de que se envíe una "
"finalización a la :abbr:`ATO (Oficina Tributaria Australiana)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1214
msgid ""
"After an employee is :ref:`terminated <payroll/au-terminate>` during the "
"year."
msgstr ""
"Después de que un empleado sea :ref:`dado de baja <payroll/au-terminate>` "
"durante el año."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1216
msgid ""
"To create an individual finalisation, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll "
"app --> Reporting --> STP Finalisation`."
msgstr ""
"Para crear una finalización individual, ve a :menuselection:`Aplicación "
"Nómina --> Informes --> Finalización STP`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1219
msgid ""
"Configure the top-half of the form in the same manner as the :ref:`typical "
"annual finalization <payroll/stp-total>`, but **do not** select the checkbox "
"next to the :guilabel:`EOFY Declaration`. Leaving this unchecked displays "
"a :guilabel:`Deadline Date` field. This is populated with the current date, "
"by default. Adjust this date if needed."
msgstr ""
"Configura la mitad superior del formulario de la misma manera que "
"la :ref:`finalización anual típica <payroll/stp-total>`, pero **no** marques "
"la casilla junto a :guilabel:`Declaración de EOFY`. Al dejar esto sin marcar "
"se muestra un campo :guilabel:`Fecha límite`. Este se rellena con la fecha "
"actual de forma predeterminada. Ajusta esta fecha si es necesario."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1224
msgid ""
"Next, manually add the employees to be finalised by clicking :guilabel:`Add "
"a line` in the :guilabel:`Employee Finalisation` tab, and selecting the "
"employee."
msgstr ""
"A continuación, añade manualmente los empleados que deben finalizarse "
"haciendo clic en :guilabel:`Añadir una línea` en la "
"pestaña :guilabel:`Finalización del empleado` y seleccionando al empleado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1228
msgid ""
"If an employee record is finalised partway through the financial year, the |"
"ATO| will **not** pre-fill the information into the employee's tax return "
"until **after** the end of the financial year."
msgstr ""
"Si se finaliza un registro de empleado a mitad del ejercicio fiscal, la |"
"ATO| **no** rellenará previamente la información en la declaración de "
"impuestos del empleado hasta **después** del final del ejercicio fiscal."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1233
msgid "ATO Security Compliance Requirements"
msgstr "Requisitos de cumplimiento de seguridad de ATO"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1235
msgid ""
"To ensure |STP| compliance, the |ATO| requires Digital Service Providers "
"(DSPs) like Odoo to adhere to strict security standards. The following "
"requirements have been implemented within the Odoo ecosystem:"
msgstr ""
"Para garantizar el cumplimiento de |STP|, la |ATO| exige que los proveedores "
"de servicios digitales (DSP) como Odoo cumplan con estrictos estándares de "
"seguridad. Los siguientes requisitos se han implementado dentro del "
"ecosistema de Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1239
msgid ""
"Audit Logging: Odoo maintains comprehensive audit logs for all payroll and "
"accounting-related records. These logs are stored in the database and "
"synchronized with our IAP server for a rolling 12-month period."
msgstr ""
"Registro de auditoría: Odoo mantiene registros de auditoría exhaustivos para "
"todos los registros relacionados con la nómina y la contabilidad. Estos "
"registros se almacenan en la base de datos y se sincronizan con nuestro "
"servidor IAP durante un período consecutivo de 12 meses."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1243
msgid ""
"Mandatory MFA: Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) is mandatory for all users "
"with access to payroll and accounting records. This security feature cannot "
"be disabled."
msgstr ""
"MFA obligatorio: La autenticación multifactor (MFA) es obligatoria para "
"todos los usuarios con acceso a los registros de nómina y contabilidad. Esta "
"característica de seguridad no se puede desactivar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1246
msgid ""
"Authentication Persistence: The \"Remember Me\" functionality is limited to "
"a maximum of 24 hours after 2FA authentication. Once this period expires, "
"Odoo will automatically log the user out and require a fresh 2FA login."
msgstr ""
"Persistencia de autenticación: La funcionalidad \"Recordarme\" está limitada "
"a un máximo de 24 horas después de la autenticación 2FA. Una vez que expire "
"este período, Odoo cerrará automáticamente la sesión del usuario y requerirá "
"un nuevo inicio de sesión 2FA."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1250
msgid ""
"Idle Session Timeout: Sessions will automatically time out after 30 minutes "
"of inactivity."
msgstr ""
"Tiempo de espera de sesión inactiva: Las sesiones caducarán automáticamente "
"después de 30 minutos de inactividad."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1252
msgid ""
"Brute Force Protection: User accounts will be locked after a maximum of 5 "
"unsuccessful login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Protección contra fuerza bruta: Las cuentas de usuario se bloquearán después "
"de un máximo de 5 intentos de inicio de sesión fallidos."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1255
msgid ""
"Onshore Data Hosting: By default, all payroll and accounting records must be "
"hosted onshore. If data is hosted offshore, the customer or partner must "
"proactively contact the |ATO|'s Digital Partnership Office (DPO)."
msgstr ""
"Alojamiento de datos en el país: De forma predeterminada, todos los "
"registros de nómina y contabilidad deben alojarse en el país. Si los datos "
"se alojan en el extranjero, el cliente o socio debe contactar proactivamente "
"con la Oficina de Asociación Digital (DPO) de |ATO|."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1259
msgid ""
"SSO Restrictions: Users are prohibited from using social media Single Sign-"
"On (SSO) to access sensitive records. While this primarily affects Facebook "
"SSO in standard Odoo, the restriction applies to all third-party social "
"media integrations."
msgstr ""
"Restricciones de SSO: Los usuarios tienen prohibido usar el inicio de sesión "
"único (SSO) de redes sociales para acceder a registros sensibles. Si bien "
"esto afecta principalmente a Facebook SSO en Odoo estándar, la restricción "
"se aplica a todas las integraciones de redes sociales de terceros."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1263
msgid ""
"Credential Expiry: Any security tokens or temporary credentials issued to "
"users with access to Odoo |STP| & SS must expire within 24 hours."
msgstr ""
"Caducidad de credenciales: Cualquier token de seguridad o credencial "
"temporal emitida a usuarios con acceso a Odoo |STP| & SS debe caducar en 24 "
"horas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:1266
msgid ""
"Encryption Integrity: Any technical modifications to encryption keys, "
"encryption at rest, or encryption in transit may jeopardize ATO compliance "
"status."
msgstr ""
"Integridad del cifrado: Cualquier modificación técnica de las claves de "
"cifrado, el cifrado en reposo o el cifrado en tránsito puede poner en "
"peligro el estado de cumplimiento de ATO."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:3
msgid "Belgium"
msgstr "Bélgica"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:8
msgid "Understanding the Belgian payslip"
msgstr "Entender la nómina belga"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:11
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:231
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:428
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:862
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1365
#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off.rst:83
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Vista general"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:13
msgid ""
"Providing employees with a clear, transparent payslip is essential for "
"compliance and employee satisfaction. This guide explains how to interpret a "
"Belgian payslip, detailing key components that impact salary calculations "
"and deductions."
msgstr ""
"Proporcionar a los empleados una nómina clara y transparente es esencial "
"para el cumplimiento y la satisfacción del empleado. Esta guía explica cómo "
"interpretar una nómina belga, detallando los componentes clave que impactan "
"los cálculos salariales y las deducciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:20
msgid ""
"The first section of the payslip contains the employee's general details. It "
"is crucial to verify the accuracy of the civil status and the number of "
"dependents, as these factors influence tax calculations. Employers can "
"ensure updates are made through their internal salary configurator or "
"employee profile management systems."
msgstr ""
"La primera sección de la nómina contiene los detalles generales del "
"empleado. Es crucial verificar la exactitud del estado civil y el número de "
"dependientes, ya que estos factores influyen en los cálculos fiscales. Los "
"empleadores pueden asegurarse de que las actualizaciones se realicen a "
"través de su configurador de salarios interno o sistemas de gestión de "
"perfiles de empleados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "How to read a payslip - General Information."
msgstr "Cómo leer una nómina - Información general."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2766
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/work_entries.rst:3
msgid "Work entries"
msgstr "Entradas de trabajo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:31
msgid ""
"This section outlines time-off applications and their impact on salary. The "
"base salary typically remains constant unless unpaid leave is taken. If an "
"employee has taken unpaid leave, parental leave, or any unexpected absence, "
"their salary will reflect the corresponding deductions."
msgstr ""
"Esta sección describe las solicitudes de tiempo libre y su impacto en el "
"salario. El salario base generalmente permanece constante a menos que se "
"tome una licencia sin goce de sueldo. Si un empleado ha tomado una licencia "
"sin goce de sueldo, licencia parental o cualquier ausencia inesperada, su "
"salario reflejará las deducciones correspondientes."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "How to read a payslip - Work Entries."
msgstr "Cómo leer una nómina - Registros de trabajo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:39
msgid "Payroll calculation"
msgstr "Cálculo de nómina"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:41
msgid ""
"The core of the payslip details various salary components, deductions, and "
"benefits. Below are the primary elements:"
msgstr ""
"El núcleo de la nómina detalla varios componentes salariales, deducciones y "
"beneficios. A continuación se presentan los elementos principales:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:44
msgid ""
"**Benefits in Kind**: If applicable, benefits in kind (such as a mobile or "
"internet subscription or a laptop) are subject to taxation and impact net "
"remuneration."
msgstr ""
"**Beneficios en especie**: Si corresponde, los beneficios en especie (como "
"una suscripción de móvil o internet o una computadora portátil) están "
"sujetos a impuestos e impactan la remuneración neta."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:47
msgid ""
"When a company car is provided for personal use, a taxable benefit (ATN) is "
"added to the employee's salary. This is determined by:"
msgstr ""
"Cuando se proporciona un automóvil de empresa para uso personal, se agrega "
"un beneficio gravable (ATN) al salario del empleado. Esto se determina por:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:50
msgid "The catalog value and age of the vehicle"
msgstr "El valor de catálogo y la antigüedad del vehículo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:51
msgid "The vehicle's CO2 emissions"
msgstr "Las emisiones de CO2 del vehículo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:53
msgid ""
"This benefit is subject to withholding tax and will be adjusted later in the "
"payroll process."
msgstr ""
"Este beneficio está sujeto a retención de impuestos y se ajustará más "
"adelante en el proceso de nómina."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Social Security contributions**: A mandatory 13.07% deduction from gross "
"salary is allocated to the National Social Security Office (ONSS). This "
"includes:"
msgstr ""
"**Contribuciones a la seguridad social**: Una deducción obligatoria del "
"13.07% del salario bruto se asigna a la Oficina Nacional de Seguridad Social "
"(ONSS). Esto incluye:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:57
msgid "Pensions: 7.5%"
msgstr "Pensiones: 7.5%"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:58
msgid "Health Insurance for Care: 3.55%"
msgstr "Seguro de salud para atención: 3.55%"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:59
msgid "Health Insurance for Benefits: 1.15%"
msgstr "Seguro de salud para beneficios: 1.15%"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:60
msgid "Unemployment: 0.87%"
msgstr "Desempleo: 0.87%"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:62
msgid ""
"Additionally, the employer contributes on average 25% of the employer's "
"contributions to the National Social Security Office."
msgstr ""
"Además, el empleador contribuye en promedio un 25% de las cotizaciones "
"patronales a la Oficina Nacional de Seguridad Social."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:64
msgid ""
"**Employment bonus**: A reduction in employee contributions based on gross "
"salary, which is phased out if the salary exceeds a specific threshold."
msgstr ""
"**Prima de empleo**: Una reducción en las cotizaciones del empleado basada "
"en el salario bruto, que se elimina progresivamente si el salario supera un "
"umbral específico."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:68
msgid ""
"`More info on job bonuses <https://www.socialsecurity.be/employer/"
"instructions/dmfa/fr/latest/instructions/deductions/workers_reductions/"
"workbonus.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Más información sobre las primas de empleo <https://www.socialsecurity.be/"
"employer/instructions/dmfa/fr/latest/instructions/deductions/"
"workers_reductions/workbonus.html>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:70
msgid ""
"**Withholding taxes**: Withholding tax rates are revised annually by the "
"`SPF Finances <https://finances.belgium.be/fr/entreprises/"
"personnel_et_remuneration/precompte_professionnel/calcul>`_."
msgstr ""
"**Retenciones fiscales**: Las tasas de retención fiscal se revisan "
"anualmente por el `SPF Finances <https://finances.belgium.be/fr/entreprises/"
"personnel_et_remuneration/precompte_professionnel/calcul>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:73
msgid "The tax amount is influenced by:"
msgstr "El importe del impuesto está influenciado por:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:75
msgid "Gross salary"
msgstr "Salario bruto"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:76
msgid "Marital status (married, legally cohabiting, or single)"
msgstr "Estado civil (casado, conviviente legal o soltero)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:77
msgid "Household composition (children or other dependents)"
msgstr "Composición del hogar (hijos u otras personas a cargo)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:79
msgid "This serves as an advance payment on professional income tax."
msgstr ""
"Esto sirve como pago anticipado del impuesto sobre la renta profesional."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Reduction in withholding tax**: A reduction based on gross salary, which "
"is ignored if salary surpasses a specific amount."
msgstr ""
"**Reducción en la retención fiscal**: Una reducción basada en el salario "
"bruto, que se ignora si el salario supera un importe específico."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:82
msgid ""
"**Special Social Security contribution**: A household income-based tax "
"applicable to all employees covered by social security."
msgstr ""
"**Contribución especial a la Seguridad Social**: Un impuesto basado en los "
"ingresos del hogar aplicable a todos los empleados cubiertos por la "
"seguridad social."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:84
msgid ""
"**Meal voucher deduction**: Employees receive meal vouchers valued for "
"instance at €8 per workday, where:"
msgstr ""
"**Deducción por vales de comida**: Los empleados reciben vales de comida "
"valorados por ejemplo en 8 € por día laboral, donde:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:87
msgid "The employer contributes €6.91"
msgstr "El empleador contribuye 6,91 €"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:88
msgid "The employee contributes €1.09"
msgstr "El empleado contribuye 1,09 €"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:91
msgid "5 worked days -> deduction of €5.45 (:math:`5\\times\\text{€}1.09`)"
msgstr ""
"5 días trabajados -> deducción de 5,45 € (:math:`5\\times\\text{€}1{,}09`)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:92
msgid "22 worked days -> deduction of €23.98 (:math:`22\\times\\text{€}1.09`)"
msgstr ""
"22 días trabajados -> deducción de 23,98 € (:math:`22\\times\\text{€}1{,}09`)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:94
msgid "Variations in this deduction impact monthly net salary."
msgstr "Las variaciones en esta deducción afectan el salario neto mensual."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:95
msgid ""
"**Representation fees**: An optional net salary component, allocated in two "
"parts:"
msgstr ""
"**Gastos de representación**: Un componente opcional del salario neto, "
"asignado en dos partes:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:97
msgid "A fixed portion, independent of working hours"
msgstr "Una parte fija, independiente de las horas de trabajo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:98
msgid "A prorated portion, adjusted for part-time schedules"
msgstr "Una parte prorrateada, ajustada para horarios de tiempo parcial"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:99
msgid ""
"**Net salary**: The final amount deposited into the employee's bank account "
"after deductions."
msgstr ""
"**Salario neto**: El importe final depositado en la cuenta bancaria del "
"empleado después de las deducciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:104
msgid "December pay"
msgstr "Pago de diciembre"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:107
msgid "Why a December settlement?"
msgstr "¿Por qué una liquidación de diciembre?"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:109
msgid ""
"An employer must pay a vacation allowance to an employee in December under "
"two conditions:"
msgstr ""
"Un empleador debe pagar una prestación por vacaciones a un empleado en "
"diciembre bajo dos condiciones:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:111
msgid ""
"If the employee has reduced their working hours during the vacation year."
msgstr ""
"Si el empleado ha reducido su jornada laboral durante el año de vacaciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:112
msgid ""
"If the employee is unable to take all their vacation days before the end of "
"the year."
msgstr ""
"Si el empleado no puede tomar todos sus días de vacaciones antes del final "
"del año."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:114
msgid ""
"In principle, employers must ensure that employees take their annual "
"vacation before December 31. However, certain circumstances may prevent "
"employees from using all their vacation days. In these cases, the employer "
"must pay the simple vacation allowance for unused days before the end of the "
"year. Additionally, if the employee has not received the double vacation "
"allowance earlier in the year (typically in May or June), they are entitled "
"to receive it."
msgstr ""
"En principio, los empleadores deben garantizar que los empleados tomen sus "
"vacaciones anuales antes del 31 de diciembre. Sin embargo, ciertas "
"circunstancias pueden impedir que los empleados usen todos sus días de "
"vacaciones. En estos casos, el empleador debe pagar la prestación simple por "
"vacaciones para los días no utilizados antes del final del año. Además, si "
"el empleado no ha recibido la prestación doble por vacaciones antes en el "
"año (típicamente en mayo o junio), tiene derecho a recibirla."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:121
msgid "Reduction of working hours"
msgstr "Reducción de jornada laboral"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:123
msgid ""
"When an employee reduces their average working hours with the same employer, "
"the employer must pay the vacation allowance in December of the year in "
"which the reduction occurs, as if the employee had left the company."
msgstr ""
"Cuando un empleado reduce su jornada laboral promedio con el mismo "
"empleador, el empleador debe pagar la prestación por vacaciones en diciembre "
"del año en que ocurre la reducción, como si el empleado hubiera dejado la "
"empresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:127
msgid "**Possible scenarios**:"
msgstr "**Escenarios posibles**:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:129
msgid "Transition to part-time work."
msgstr "Transición a trabajo a tiempo parcial."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:130
msgid "Partial career break."
msgstr "Pausa parcial en la carrera profesional."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:131
msgid "Thematic leave on a part-time basis."
msgstr "Permiso temático a tiempo parcial."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:132
msgid "Partial return to work after a full incapacity period."
msgstr "Regreso parcial al trabajo después de un período de incapacidad total."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:134
msgid ""
"The settlement is calculated based on the previous vacation year's earnings "
"and includes:"
msgstr ""
"La liquidación se calcula en base a los ingresos del año de vacaciones "
"anterior e incluye:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:136
msgid ""
"**Simple vacation allowance**: 7.67% of the yearly gross salary from the "
"previous year, including any fictitious salary for assimilated interruption "
"days, minus the simple vacation allowance already paid during the vacation "
"year."
msgstr ""
"**Prestación simple por vacaciones**: 7,67% del salario bruto anual del año "
"anterior, incluido cualquier salario ficticio por días de interrupción "
"asimilados, menos la prestación simple por vacaciones ya pagada durante el "
"año de vacaciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:139
msgid ""
"**Double vacation allowance**: 7.67% of the yearly gross salary from the "
"previous year, including any fictitious salary for assimilated interruption "
"days, minus the double vacation allowance already paid during the vacation "
"year."
msgstr ""
"**Prestación doble por vacaciones**: 7,67% del salario bruto anual del año "
"anterior, incluido cualquier salario ficticio por días de interrupción "
"asimilados, menos la prestación doble por vacaciones ya pagada durante el "
"año de vacaciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:143
msgid ""
"If all vacation days have been taken before the reduction in working hours, "
"no additional calculation is required."
msgstr ""
"Si todos los días de vacaciones se han tomado antes de la reducción de "
"jornada laboral, no se requiere ningún cálculo adicional."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:147
msgid "Inability to use vacation days"
msgstr "Imposibilidad de usar los días de vacaciones"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:149
msgid ""
"As a general rule, all vacation days must be used within the vacation year. "
"However, if an employee is unable to take all their vacation due to force "
"majeure or specific suspension reasons, the employer must pay the following "
"by December 31:"
msgstr ""
"Como regla general, todos los días de vacaciones deben usarse dentro del año "
"de vacaciones. Sin embargo, si un empleado no puede tomar todas sus "
"vacaciones debido a fuerza mayor o motivos específicos de suspensión, el "
"empleador debe pagar lo siguiente antes del 31 de diciembre:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:153
msgid ""
"**Simple vacation allowance** for unused days, based on the December salary."
msgstr ""
"**Subsidio de vacaciones simple** para días no utilizados, basado en el "
"salario de diciembre."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:154
msgid ""
"**Double vacation allowance** if it has not yet been paid, based on the "
"December salary."
msgstr ""
"**Subsidio de vacaciones doble** si aún no ha sido pagado, basado en el "
"salario de diciembre."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:156
msgid "**Eligible reasons include**:"
msgstr "**Las razones elegibles incluyen**:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:158
msgid "Common illness or accident."
msgstr "Enfermedad o accidente común."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:159
msgid "Work accident or occupational disease."
msgstr "Accidente laboral o enfermedad profesional."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:160
msgid ""
"Maternity leave, paternity leave (converted maternity leave), prophylactic "
"leave."
msgstr ""
"Baja por maternidad, baja por paternidad (baja por maternidad convertida), "
"baja profiláctica."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:161
msgid "Birth, adoption, or reception leave."
msgstr "Baja por nacimiento, adopción o acogida."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:162
msgid "Parental leave or protective maternity leave measures."
msgstr "Baja parental o medidas de protección por maternidad."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:165
msgid "New rule (effective end of 2024)"
msgstr "Nueva norma (vigente a finales de 2024)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:167
msgid ""
"Employees unable to take vacation due to the above reasons (except force "
"majeure or protective maternity leave measures) can carry over unused days "
"for up to 24 months. Since the vacation allowance is already paid in "
"December of the vacation year, no additional payment will be made when the "
"carried-over days are used."
msgstr ""
"Los empleados que no puedan tomar vacaciones debido a las razones anteriores "
"(excepto fuerza mayor o medidas de protección por maternidad) pueden "
"trasladar los días no utilizados hasta 24 meses. Dado que el subsidio de "
"vacaciones ya se paga en diciembre del año de vacaciones, no se realizará "
"ningún pago adicional cuando se utilicen los días trasladados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:173
msgid "Employer payment responsibilities"
msgstr "Responsabilidades de pago del empleador"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:175
msgid ""
"The employer must pay any outstanding simple vacation allowance based on "
"7.67% of the gross salary from the previous year. However, an exit vacation "
"allowance based on the current year's gross salary is not due."
msgstr ""
"El empleador debe pagar cualquier subsidio de vacaciones simple pendiente "
"basado en el 7,67% del salario bruto del año anterior. Sin embargo, no se "
"debe un subsidio de vacaciones de salida basado en el salario bruto del año "
"actual."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:179
msgid ""
"If an employee reduces their working hours and continues in the same role "
"the following year, an additional vacation allowance calculation may be "
"required in December."
msgstr ""
"Si un empleado reduce su jornada laboral y continúa en el mismo puesto el "
"año siguiente, puede ser necesario un cálculo adicional del subsidio de "
"vacaciones en diciembre."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:183
msgid "Example calculation"
msgstr "Ejemplo de cálculo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:185
msgid "In 2013, an employee works full-time (5 days per week)."
msgstr "En 2013, un empleado trabaja a tiempo completo (5 días por semana)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:186
msgid ""
"In 2014, the employee works full-time until June 30, then switches to part-"
"time (5 half-days per week)."
msgstr ""
"En 2014, el empleado trabaja a tiempo completo hasta el 30 de junio y luego "
"cambia a tiempo parcial (5 medios días por semana)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:188
msgid ""
"The employee takes vacation in August 2014 under the new part-time regime "
"(20 half-days over 4 weeks)."
msgstr ""
"El empleado toma vacaciones en agosto de 2014 bajo el nuevo régimen de "
"tiempo parcial (20 medios días durante 4 semanas)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:190
msgid ""
"They receive a simple vacation allowance for 20 half-days and a double "
"vacation allowance equivalent to 92% of their monthly salary."
msgstr ""
"Recibe un subsidio de vacaciones simple por 20 medios días y un subsidio de "
"vacaciones doble equivalente al 92% de su salario mensual."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:192
msgid ""
"In December 2014, the employee receives additional simple (7.67%) and double "
"(7.67%) vacation allowances based on 2013's gross salary, minus previously "
"paid amounts."
msgstr ""
"En diciembre de 2014, el empleado recibe subsidios de vacaciones simples "
"(7,67%) y dobles (7,67%) adicionales basados en el salario bruto de 2013, "
"menos los montos previamente pagados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:194
msgid ""
"In 2015, if the employee continues part-time, they receive vacation based on "
"part-time hours plus 5 full-time vacation days from the 2014 vacation year."
msgstr ""
"En 2015, si el empleado continúa a tiempo parcial, recibe vacaciones basadas "
"en horas de tiempo parcial más 5 días de vacaciones a tiempo completo del "
"año de vacaciones 2014."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:196
msgid ""
"A second settlement in December 2015 includes additional simple (7.67%) and "
"double (7.67%) vacation allowances based on the 2014 gross salary, minus "
"previously paid amounts."
msgstr ""
"Un segundo pago en diciembre de 2015 incluye prestaciones de vacaciones "
"simples (7,67%) y dobles (7,67%) adicionales basadas en el salario bruto de "
"2014, menos los montos pagados previamente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1650
msgid "How to do it in Odoo"
msgstr "Cómo hacerlo en Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:202
msgid ""
"On a classic :doc:`payslip <../payslips>` issued in December, press "
"the :guilabel:`Compute December Holiday Pay` button to open a configuration "
"wizard."
msgstr ""
"En una :doc:`nómina <../payslips>` clásica emitida en diciembre, presiona el "
"botón :guilabel:`Calcular pago de vacaciones de diciembre` para abrir un "
"asistente de configuración."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:205
msgid ""
"Based on the allocated and requested time off, the :guilabel:`Simple Holiday "
"Pay N-1` and :guilabel:`Double Holiday Pay N-1` for the December payslip are "
"computed (and editable for manual encoding). Click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
"confirm."
msgstr ""
"Según las ausencias asignadas y solicitadas, se calculan (y son editables "
"para codificación manual) :guilabel:`Pago de vacaciones simple N-1` "
"y :guilabel:`Pago de vacaciones doble N-1` para la nómina de diciembre. Haz "
"clic en :guilabel:`Validar` para confirmar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "December Pay Amount."
msgstr "Monto del pago de diciembre."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:212
msgid ""
"After validation, two additional inputs are stored on the payslip, and the "
"payslip is re-computed to take those new remunerations into account."
msgstr ""
"Después de la validación, se almacenan dos entradas adicionales en la "
"nómina, y la nómina se recalcula para tener en cuenta esas nuevas "
"remuneraciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:215
msgid "The simple holiday pay is included into the gross remuneration."
msgstr "El pago de vacaciones simple se incluye en la remuneración bruta."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "December Pay Simple."
msgstr "Pago simple de diciembre."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:220
msgid ""
"The double holiday pay is computed separately and included into the net "
"amount."
msgstr ""
"El pago de vacaciones doble se calcula por separado y se incluye en el monto "
"neto."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "December Pay Double."
msgstr "Pago doble de diciembre."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:228
msgid "Departure: holiday attests"
msgstr "Salida: certificados de vacaciones"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:233
msgid ""
"In Belgium, when an employee leaves a company, the employer is required to "
"provide vacation attestations. These documents help the new employer "
"determine the employee's vacation entitlements and any vacation pay due. "
"Odoo facilitates the automatic generation of these attestations based on "
"payroll and time-off data."
msgstr ""
"En Bélgica, cuando un empleado deja una empresa, el empleador está obligado "
"a proporcionar certificados de vacaciones. Estos documentos ayudan al nuevo "
"empleador a determinar los derechos de vacaciones del empleado y cualquier "
"pago de vacaciones adeudado. Odoo facilita la generación automática de estos "
"certificados según los datos de nómina y ausencias."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:239
msgid "Types of attestations"
msgstr "Tipos de certificados"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:241
msgid "Odoo generates two types of vacation attestations:"
msgstr "Odoo genera dos tipos de certificados de vacaciones:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:243
msgid ""
"**For the previous year (N-1)**: If the employee has not yet taken all the "
"vacation days from the previous year."
msgstr ""
"**Para el año anterior (N-1)**: Si el empleado aún no ha tomado todos los "
"días de vacaciones del año anterior."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:245
msgid ""
"**For the current year (N)**: Covering the vacation rights accrued in the "
"year of departure."
msgstr ""
"**Para el año actual (N)**: Cubriendo los derechos de vacaciones acumulados "
"en el año de salida."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:247
msgid "Each attestation includes details such as:"
msgstr "Cada certificado incluye detalles como:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:249
msgid "The period the employee was employed."
msgstr "El período en que el empleado estuvo empleado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:250
msgid "Agreed working time and any modifications."
msgstr "Tiempo de trabajo acordado y cualquier modificación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:251
msgid "Gross amounts of single and double vacation pay paid."
msgstr "Montos brutos del pago de vacaciones simple y doble pagados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:252
msgid "Social security contributions paid by the employer."
msgstr "Cotizaciones a la seguridad social pagadas por el empleador."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:253
msgid "Number of vacation days already taken."
msgstr "Número de días de vacaciones ya tomados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:254
msgid "Additional (European) vacation pay and days."
msgstr "Pago y días de vacaciones adicionales (europeos)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:257
msgid "Calculation logic in Odoo"
msgstr "Lógica de cálculo en Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:259
msgid ""
"Odoo computes the attestations based on payroll and leave data. The main "
"calculations include:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo calcula las certificaciones basándose en datos de nómina y ausencias. "
"Los cálculos principales incluyen:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:261
msgid "**Retrieving payroll and leave records**"
msgstr "**Recuperar registros de nómina y ausencias**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:263
msgid ""
"The system identifies the employee's payroll records for the current and "
"previous years."
msgstr ""
"El sistema identifica los registros de nómina del empleado para el año "
"actual y anterior."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:264
msgid "It retrieves validated leave requests and allocations."
msgstr "Recupera las solicitudes y asignaciones de ausencias validadas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:266
msgid "**Computing gross remuneration**"
msgstr "**Calcular la remuneración bruta**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:268
msgid ""
"The gross annual salary for both the current and previous years is computed "
"from payroll records."
msgstr ""
"El salario bruto anual tanto del año actual como del anterior se calcula a "
"partir de los registros de nómina."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:270
msgid "The average monthly salary is calculated for unpaid leave adjustments."
msgstr ""
"El salario mensual promedio se calcula para ajustes de ausencias no "
"remuneradas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:272
msgid "**Time-off calculations**"
msgstr "**Cálculos de tiempo libre**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:274
msgid ""
"The number of vacation days taken and allocated in the current year is "
"determined."
msgstr ""
"Se determina el número de días de vacaciones tomados y asignados en el año "
"actual."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:275
msgid "Unpaid leave days are accounted for separately."
msgstr "Los días de ausencia no remunerada se contabilizan por separado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:277
msgid "**Fictitious remuneration calculation**"
msgstr "**Cálculo de remuneración ficticia**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:279
msgid ""
"If unpaid leave was taken, Odoo computes a fictitious remuneration "
"adjustment using the formula:"
msgstr ""
"Si se tomó una ausencia no remunerada, Odoo calcula un ajuste de "
"remuneración ficticia usando la fórmula:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:282
msgid ""
"\\text{Fictitious Remuneration} = (\\text{Unpaid Leave Days} \\times\n"
"\\text{Average Monthly Salary} \\times 3) \\div (13 \\times 5)"
msgstr ""
"\\text{Remuneración Ficticia} = (\\text{Días de Ausencia no Remunerada} "
"\\times\n"
"\\text{Salario Mensual Promedio} \\times 3) \\div (13 \\times 5)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:288
msgid "**Generating the final attestation**"
msgstr "**Generar la certificación final**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:290
msgid "Odoo creates a payroll entry reflecting the vacation pay due."
msgstr ""
"Odoo crea un registro de nómina que refleja el pago de vacaciones adeudado."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:291
msgid "The attestation document is generated and can be printed or exported."
msgstr ""
"Se genera el documento de certificación y se puede imprimir o exportar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:293
msgid "Two payslips are created:"
msgstr "Se crean dos recibos de nómina:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:295
msgid "**Payslip for the current year** (`termination_payslip_n`)"
msgstr "**Recibo de nómina para el año actual** (`termination_payslip_n`)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:297
msgid ""
"This payslip covers the employee's last salary period in the year of "
"termination."
msgstr ""
"Este recibo de nómina cubre el último periodo salarial del empleado en el "
"año de terminación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:299
msgid "**Payslip for the previous year** (`termination_payslip_n1`)"
msgstr "**Recibo de nómina para el año anterior** (`termination_payslip_n1`)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:301
msgid ""
"The one accounts the amount of money converted from the untaken time off of "
"previous year."
msgstr ""
"Este contabiliza la cantidad de dinero convertida de las ausencias no "
"tomadas del año anterior."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:303
msgid ""
"Each payslip is generated using the appropriate payroll structure, ensuring "
"correct calculations for all entitlements and deductions."
msgstr ""
"Cada recibo de nómina se genera utilizando la estructura de nómina "
"apropiada, asegurando cálculos correctos para todos los derechos y "
"deducciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:306
msgid ""
"Before computing the final payment, the system gathers necessary payroll "
"data:"
msgstr ""
"Antes de calcular el pago final, el sistema recopila los datos de nómina "
"necesarios:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:308
msgid "**Annual gross salary calculation**"
msgstr "**Cálculo del salario bruto anual**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:310
msgid ""
"To estimate the employee's **annual gross salary**, the system looks for the "
"most recent validated monthly payslip. If a payslip is found, the **gross "
"salary** from that payslip is multiplied by 12 to get an annual estimate. If "
"no payslip exists, the annual gross salary is set to **zero**."
msgstr ""
"Para estimar el **salario bruto anual** del empleado, el sistema busca el "
"recibo de nómina mensual validado más reciente. Si se encuentra un recibo de "
"nómina, el **salario bruto** de ese recibo se multiplica por 12 para obtener "
"una estimación anual. Si no existe ningún recibo de nómina, el salario bruto "
"anual se establece en **cero**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:315
msgid "**European leave recovery**"
msgstr "**Recuperación de vacaciones europeas**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:317
msgid ""
"The system retrieves all **European leave days (LEAVE216)** taken by the "
"employee during the current year. It then calculates the **total amount paid "
"for these leaves** and determines how much should be deducted."
msgstr ""
"El sistema recupera todos los **días de vacaciones europeas (LEAVE216)** "
"tomados por el empleado durante el año actual. Luego calcula el **importe "
"total pagado por estas ausencias** y determina cuánto debe deducirse."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:321
msgid "The deduction follows these principles:"
msgstr "La deducción sigue estos principios:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:323
msgid ""
"If an employee has taken **European holidays (additional vacation days)**, "
"the amount paid in advance must be recovered."
msgstr ""
"Si un empleado ha tomado **vacaciones europeas (días de vacaciones "
"adicionales)**, el importe pagado por adelantado debe recuperarse."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:325
msgid "The recovery is either:"
msgstr "La recuperación se realiza mediante:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:327
msgid "Deducted from **the double vacation pay (85%)** for the next year."
msgstr ""
"Deducción de **la paga doble de vacaciones (85%)** para el próximo año."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:328
msgid ""
"Or, if the employee leaves, deducted from the final termination payslip."
msgstr ""
"O, si el empleado se va, se deduce del recibo de nómina final de terminación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:330
msgid "If leave has been taken, the **termination certificate** must specify:"
msgstr ""
"Si se han tomado ausencias, el **certificado de terminación** debe "
"especificar:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:332
msgid "The **number of European leave days** already granted."
msgstr "El **número de días de vacaciones europeas** ya concedidos."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:333
msgid "The **gross allowance** corresponding to these days."
msgstr "La **asignación bruta** correspondiente a estos días."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:335
msgid ""
"To ensure fairness, the system first checks whether a deduction has already "
"been applied in the **double vacation pay**. If so, only the remaining "
"amount is deducted from the final payslip."
msgstr ""
"Para garantizar la equidad, el sistema primero verifica si ya se ha aplicado "
"una deducción en la **paga doble de vacaciones**. Si es así, solo se deduce "
"el importe restante del recibo de nómina final."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:338
msgid ""
"Once the required values are determined, they are recorded in the payslip as "
"**additional payroll inputs**:"
msgstr ""
"Una vez que se determinan los valores requeridos, se registran en la nómina "
"como **entradas de nómina adicionales**:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:341
msgid ""
"**Gross salary reference**: Includes the final salary amount plus any "
"fictitious remuneration."
msgstr ""
"**Referencia de salario bruto**: Incluye el importe del salario final más "
"cualquier remuneración ficticia."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:342
msgid ""
"**European leave deduction**: Deducts the previously paid European leave "
"amounts."
msgstr ""
"**Deducción de ausencia europea**: Deduce los importes de ausencia europea "
"previamente pagados."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:343
msgid ""
"**Other inputs**: Allocates time off taken, taxable amounts, and any "
"outstanding allocations."
msgstr ""
"**Otras entradas**: Asigna ausencias tomadas, importes imponibles y "
"cualquier asignación pendiente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:345
msgid ""
"After setting these values, the system **computes the payslip** to ensure "
"all deductions and payments are correctly applied."
msgstr ""
"Después de establecer estos valores, el sistema **calcula la nómina** para "
"garantizar que todas las deducciones y pagos se apliquen correctamente."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:348
msgid ""
"This process ensures that the final **termination payslip** takes into "
"account all salary components, including **annual gross pay, European leave "
"recovery, and any unpaid entitlements**. Odoo retrieves past payslips and "
"time-off records to ensure compliance with **Belgian payroll regulations**."
msgstr ""
"Este proceso garantiza que la **nómina de finiquito** final tenga en cuenta "
"todos los componentes salariales, incluidos **el salario bruto anual, la "
"recuperación de ausencia europea y cualquier derecho no pagado**. Odoo "
"recupera nóminas anteriores y registros de ausencias para garantizar el "
"cumplimiento de **las regulaciones de nómina belgas**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:353
msgid ""
"By automating this process, Odoo minimizes manual intervention, reducing "
"errors and ensuring employees receive the correct termination payments."
msgstr ""
"Al automatizar este proceso, Odoo minimiza la intervención manual, "
"reduciendo errores y garantizando que los empleados reciban los pagos de "
"finiquito correctos."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:357
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:609
msgid "How does it work in Odoo?"
msgstr "¿Cómo funciona en Odoo?"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:359
msgid ""
"In Odoo, to access the holiday attests process, go to the employee form view "
"and click on :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Action)` then :guilabel:`Departure: "
"Holiday Attests` or navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll --> Reporting --> "
"Departure: Holiday Attests`."
msgstr ""
"En Odoo, para acceder al proceso de certificados de vacaciones, ve a la "
"vista de formulario del empleado y haz clic en :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Acción` y luego en :guilabel:`Salida: Certificados de "
"vacaciones` o navega a :menuselection:`Nómina --> Informes --> Salida: "
"Certificados de vacaciones`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:363
msgid ""
"In the wizard that appears, you can see all the payslips over the current "
"and last year, the time off requests and allocations. You can also encode "
"the unpaid time off you would like to declare on that holiday attest."
msgstr ""
"En el asistente que aparece, puedes ver todas las nóminas del año actual y "
"del año pasado, las solicitudes y asignaciones de ausencias. También puedes "
"codificar las ausencias no pagadas que deseas declarar en ese certificado de "
"vacaciones."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:367
msgid ""
"Once you're ready, click the :guilabel:`Validate & Compute holiday attests` "
"button. Two payslips are generated for each considered period (N and N-1)."
msgstr ""
"Cuando estés listo, haz clic en el botón :guilabel:`Validar y calcular "
"certificados de vacaciones`. Se generan dos nóminas para cada período "
"considerado (N y N-1)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:370
msgid ""
"Once validated, two :file:`.pdf` documents are generated. One **classic "
"payslip** and one **holiday attests** for the future employer."
msgstr ""
"Una vez validados, se generan dos documentos :file:`.pdf`. Una **nómina "
"clásica** y un **certificado de vacaciones** para el futuro empleador."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Departure Holiday Attests Payslips."
msgstr "Nóminas de certificados de vacaciones de salida."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Departure Holiday Attests Time off."
msgstr "Ausencias de certificados de vacaciones de salida."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Departure Holiday Attests Unpaid."
msgstr "Ausencias no pagadas de certificados de vacaciones de salida."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:387
msgid ""
"In our example, the employee also took one European time off during the N-"
"year."
msgstr ""
"En nuestro ejemplo, el empleado también tomó una ausencia europea durante el "
"año N."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:389
msgid "For year N-1, you can see that all legal time off were taken."
msgstr ""
"Para el año N-1, puedes ver que se tomaron todas las ausencias legales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Departure Holiday Attests Attest N-1."
msgstr "Certificado N-1 de certificados de vacaciones de salida."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Departure Holiday Attests Payslip N-1."
msgstr "Nómina N-1 de certificados de vacaciones de salida."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:397
msgid ""
"For year N, you can also see the number off additional time off (European) "
"and already taken legal time off are taken into account as well."
msgstr ""
"Para el año N, también puedes ver que se tiene en cuenta el número de "
"ausencias adicionales (europeas) y las ausencias legales ya tomadas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Departure Holiday Attests Attest N."
msgstr "Departure Holiday Attests Attest N."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Departure Holiday Attests Payslip N."
msgstr "Departure Holiday Attests Payslip N."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:407
msgid "Important Notes"
msgstr "Notas importantes"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:409
msgid ""
"By using Odoo's automated attestation generation, companies can ensure "
"compliance with Belgian labor laws while reducing manual administrative work."
msgstr ""
"Al usar la generación automática de certificados de Odoo, las empresas "
"pueden garantizar el cumplimiento de las leyes laborales belgas mientras "
"reducen el trabajo administrativo manual."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:413
msgid "The feature is only available for companies registered in Belgium."
msgstr "La función solo está disponible para empresas registradas en Bélgica."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:414
msgid ""
"If the notice period is not set for an employee, Odoo will prompt for this "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Si el período de preaviso no está configurado para un empleado, Odoo "
"solicitará esta información."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:415
msgid ""
"Employers must ensure vacation attestations are provided before the employee "
"needs to submit them to their new employer or the ONEM."
msgstr ""
"Los empleadores deben asegurarse de que los certificados de vacaciones se "
"proporcionen antes de que el empleado necesite presentarlos a su nuevo "
"empleador o al ONEM."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:421
msgid "Departure: notice period & termination fees"
msgstr "Salida: período de preaviso y tasas de terminación"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:423
msgid ""
"This documentation explains how the employee departure process works in the "
"application, focusing on the notice period calculation and severance pay "
"when the employee does not serve their notice period."
msgstr ""
"Esta documentación explica cómo funciona el proceso de salida del empleado "
"en la aplicación, centrándose en el cálculo del período de preaviso y la "
"indemnización por despido cuando el empleado no cumple su período de "
"preaviso."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:430
msgid ""
"This module helps manage employee departures by determining the correct "
"notice period based on seniority, departure reasons, and specific country "
"regulations (Belgium). It also calculates severance pay when the employee "
"does not work during their notice period."
msgstr ""
"Este módulo ayuda a gestionar las salidas de empleados determinando el "
"período de preaviso correcto según la antigüedad, las razones de salida y "
"las regulaciones específicas del país (Bélgica). También calcula la "
"indemnización por despido cuando el empleado no trabaja durante su período "
"de preaviso."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:435
msgid "Key features"
msgstr "Características principales"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:437
msgid "Automatic calculation of notice period start and end dates."
msgstr ""
"Cálculo automático de las fechas de inicio y fin del período de preaviso."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:438
msgid "Consideration of public holidays and company-specific schedules."
msgstr "Consideración de días festivos y horarios específicos de la empresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:439
msgid ""
"Calculation of severance pay based on company policies and government rules."
msgstr ""
"Cálculo de la indemnización por despido según las políticas de la empresa y "
"las normas gubernamentales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:440
msgid "Generation of a final payslip including termination fees."
msgstr "Generación de una nómina final que incluye las tasas de terminación."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:443
msgid "Notice period calculation"
msgstr "Cálculo del período de preaviso"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:445
msgid "The notice period depends on several factors:"
msgstr "El período de preaviso depende de varios factores:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:447
msgid "The employee's seniority in the company."
msgstr "La antigüedad del empleado en la empresa."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:448
msgid "The reason for departure (resignation, dismissal, retirement, etc.)."
msgstr "El motivo de la salida (renuncia, despido, jubilación, etc.)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:449
msgid "Whether the employee works during the notice period or not."
msgstr "Si el empleado trabaja durante el período de preaviso o no."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:450
msgid "The salary level before January 1, 2014 (for some cases)."
msgstr "El nivel salarial antes del 1 de enero de 2014 (para algunos casos)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:452
msgid ""
"The notice period starts on the first Monday after the departure date unless "
"a specific rule applies (e.g., a mandatory waiting period of three days for "
"certain dismissals)."
msgstr ""
"El período de preaviso comienza el primer lunes después de la fecha de "
"salida, a menos que se aplique una regla específica (por ejemplo, un período "
"de espera obligatorio de tres días para ciertos despidos)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:456
msgid "Notice duration rules"
msgstr "Reglas de duración del preaviso"

