"Next, check the various totals (gross pay, employee taxes, benefits, "
"employer taxes, net salaries), then click :guilabel:`Compute Sheet` to "
"update the salary calculations, if there were edits. If everything is "
"correct, click :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"A continuación, verifica los distintos totales (pago bruto, impuestos del "
"empleado, beneficios, impuestos del empleador, salarios netos), luego haz "
"clic en :guilabel:`Calcular hoja` para actualizar los cálculos salariales, "
"si hubo ediciones. Si todo es correcto, haz clic en :guilabel:`Validar`."

