#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:456
msgid "Understanding the Indian Payslip"
msgstr "Comprender la nómina india"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:458
msgid ""
"This payslip provides detailed information on allowances, deductions, "
"compliance requirements, and benefits. It helps employees understand how "
"their salary is calculated, the statutory and organizational deductions "
"applied, and the benefits they are entitled to, ensuring transparency and "
"trust in the payroll process."
msgstr ""
"Esta nómina proporciona información detallada sobre asignaciones, "
"deducciones, requisitos de cumplimiento y beneficios. Ayuda a los empleados "
"a entender cómo se calcula su salario, las deducciones legales y "
"organizacionales aplicadas, y los beneficios a los que tienen derecho, "
"garantizando transparencia y confianza en el proceso de nómina."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:464
