"para empleados, incluyendo regulaciones nacionales y provinciales."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:13
msgid ""
"Before configuring the Saudi Arabia localization, refer to the "
"general :doc:`payroll <../../payroll>` documentation, which includes the "
"basic information for all localizations, as well as all universal settings "
"and fields."
