#~ msgid ""
#~ "The Hong Kong payroll localization ensures all salary computations "
#~ "strictly comply with the `Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) <https://"
#~ "www.labour.gov.hk/eng/legislat/content2.htm>`_ and `Inland Revenue "
#~ "Department (IRD) <https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/erc.htm>`_ requirements. "
